snippet.title: Aashram Chapter 2 - The Dark Side | Official Trailer | Bobby Deol | Prakash Jha | MX Player
snippet.description:
Rakshak ya Bhakshak?
Paavan ya Paapi?
Kya hai Kashipur waale Baba Nirala ka asli roop? 

Hoga khulasa 11-11-2020 ko, #AashramChapter2 mein!

#Aashram #MXOriginalSeries #MXPlayer

Directed by Prakash Jha

Key Cast: Bobby Deol, Aaditi Pohankar, Chandan Roy Sanyal, Darshan Kumaar, Anupria Goenka, Adhyayan Summan, Tridha Choudhury, Vikram Kochhar, Tushar Pandey, Sachin Shroff, Anuritta Jha, Rajeev Siddhartha, Parinitaa Seth, Tanmaay Ranjan, Preeti Sood, Jahangir Khan, Kanupriya Gupta and Navdeep Tomar

About Aashram Chapter 2:
As the true face of Kashipur waale Baba Nirala unfurls, various hidden dark secrets of Aashram are discovered by the Sub-Inspector Ujagar Singh and Constable Sadhu. On the other hand, by roping in a  famous pop-star Tinka Singh, Baba rises as the icon of the youth. With this rising popularity and fame, Baba becomes the center of attraction for both political candidates who are contesting for the upcoming state elections. 

Pammi, who has turned into a blind devotee of Baba, continues to flourish inside the Aashram. How far will her blind faith for Baba sustain? After all, behind his holy image of a messiah, lies the true monster, who exploits young girls. Will Pammi’s fate be any different from all the other girls who fell victim to this deep nexus?

ASLE - Gurman Sandhu | Gur Sidhu | Jassi Lohka | Brown Town Music | New Punjabi Song 2020

Lyrics:

das ta shi tu kinu kinu veham ho gya , kihda dunia te poora poora time ho gya ,oh das kihde dil vich shak balliye , kehra jatt to shudalu tera hath balliye , ni tu poori poori chal pakh balliye , te mai appe suljalu masle 

jehrhya hatha ch billo tera hath ni ohna hatha vich khede asle 

pehla ghumda si sharayam shehar tere ch velly pura velly pura bhau bnke, baki sochya si katt laini mai zindgi tere nal tere sau bnke ,Pyar tera dil ch vsa ho gya , aayi zindgi ch change subah ho gya , sutte si jo tere kehan utte jatt ne tere lyi fer dabb nal kass lye , 



gur sidhu music

oh msa msa parche nbed sohniye banya si passport tere yaar da lagda jangal paina fer launa ni , likhya na lage daana paani bahr da , taude bhann ke purane sand rakh lye sirane , ni tu karde ishara jehre ulje aa taane , oh jatt tera jeonda rabb de aa bhaane keh gye sade nal jo kithe vass lye ,


jehrhya hatha ch billo tera hath ni ohna hatha vich khede asle 

Likh Lainda Naam tere sohna sohniye , bhawe mannya jatta da putt ghatt parhya ,
dabb rakhya ni photya kron de lyi , ni mai parh du vichalo jehra vich arhya , yaar 3-4 rehnde bas phone udeek de, akhi mai dikhadu tenu saare cheekde , ni tu jassi lohka jassi lohka reh jappdi munda marda tere te raffle , 


jehrhya hatha ch billo tera hath ni ohna hatha vich khede asle.

snippet.title: महागठबंधन मुख्यमंत्री पद उम्मीदवार श्री तेजस्वी यादव को सिवान से लाइव सुनिए!
snippet.description: Rashtriya Janta Dal locates itself in the collective aspirations of people and communities striving to carve out a society based on the premises of social justice and secularism. Since its inception Rashtriya Janta Dal is relentlessly working as the voice of the socially and economically downtrodden sections of the society. The RJD believes in working on and propagating socialist politics and towrds this end the party has been developing solidarity network of landless labourers, peasants and farmers other weaker groups as well as progressive people from other sections of society. Drawing inspiration from Gandhian values as well as following in the great tradition of the socialist leaders, RJD strongly stands against communalism in any form. The party believes that the right of peaceful and democratic dissent including Satyagraha/ non-violent resistance is a fundamental right of the people.

snippet.title: Juventus vs. Barcelona: Extended Highlights | UCL on CBS Sports
snippet.description:
Heading into the match all of the talk was surrounding Juventus and the fact they would be missing their superstar, Cristiano Ronaldo for the second straight UEFA Champions League Group stage match. Barcelona though quickly turned the conversation to just how potent their attack can be surging out to a 1-0 lead in the first 15 minutes.

In the 14’, Ousmane Dembélé rifled a beautiful, and slightly lucky, shot off of a Juventus defender that found its way to the top left corner of the goal leaving the keeper no chance at making the save. Juventus though fired right back quickly creating a one on one chance with the Barcelona keeper, Álvaro Morata did put it home but the goal was called off for being offside which VAR confirmed. Juventus had another real threat this time by Morata in the 30’, however he timed his run a hair early and when the goal found the back of the net, the flag was up negating the chance. 
To start the second half Juventus picked up right where they left off in the first half. In the 56’ they powered it into the back of the net, but after going to VAR it was ruled a no goal due to offside. 
Barcelona iced the game in stoppage time with a Messi penalty goal to give them the 2-0 win. 

Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access:
http://bit.ly/ucloncbssports

snippet.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise to new heights in Apex Legends Season 7 on the floating city of Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

There’s a whole new world waiting to be explored. The stakes are higher and the falls are deadlier on Olympus. New Legend Horizon understands the gravity of the situation, and she’s sure to give the other Legends a lift -- whether they want it or not. Plus hop on Olympus’s floating Trident vehicles, grab the latest Battle Pass, ascend to the top of Ranked, and build your community with Clubs. Up your game when Season 7 releases on November 4.

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. And play on Steam when Season 7 launches on November 4 !

localizations.de-DE.description:
Starte deinen Höhenflug in Apex Legends Saison 7 auf der schwebenden Stadt Olympus  http://x.ea.com/65921

Erkunde eine völlig neue Welt. Auf Olympus ist der Einsatz höher und jeder Sturz noch tödlicher. Die neue Legende, Horizon, weiß um den Ernst der Lage und hilft den anderen Legenden auf die Sprünge – ob sie wollen oder nicht. Drehe auf Olympus außerdem eine Runde mit den schwebenden Tridents, hol dir den neuesten Battle Pass, klettere an die Spitze der Rangliste und baue mit Clubs deine eigene Community auf. Bringe dein Spiel voran, wenn Saison 7 am 5. November erscheint.

localizations.no.description:
Nå nye høyder i den 7. sesongen av Apex Legends, som finner sted i den svevende byen Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden venter på å bli utforsket. Enda mer står på spill og høydene blir enda farligere på Olympus. Den nye legenden Horizon forstår byrden situasjonen byr på, og hun kan gi de andre legendene et løft – enten de vil det eller ei. Hopp ombord i de svevende Trident-kjøretøyene på Olympus, skaff deg spillets nye Battle Pass, nå toppen i rangerte kamper og etabler ditt eget fellesskap med klubber. Ta spillet til nye høyder når sesong 7 lanseres 4. november.

localizations.it.description:
Raggiungi nuove vette ed esplora la città sospesa di Olympus nella Stagione 7 di Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un mondo inesplorato ti aspetta. A Olympus, il pericolo è sempre in agguato e gli errori non lasciano scampo. La nuova leggenda Horizon conosce la... gravità della situazione ed è pronta a tirare su le altre leggende, che lo vogliano o meno. Usa i Trident per spostarti in giro per la mappa, ottieni il nuovo pass battaglia, scala le vette della competizione nella modalità Classificata e crea la tua community con i club. Dai il massimo nella Stagione 7, in arrivo il 4 novembre.

Nowy świat czeka na odkrycie. Na Olimpie stawki są większe, a upadki bardziej bolesne. Nowa legenda, Horizon, dobrze zdaje sobie sprawę z wagi sytuacji i chętnie pomoże pozostałym legendom – czy tego chcą, czy nie. Wsiądźcie do latających pojazdów Olimpu, Trójzębów, i sprawcie sobie nową przepustkę bojową, pnijcie się na szczyt rankingu i rozwijajcie społeczność w Klubach. localizations.ja.description:
空中都市オリンパスへ向かい、「エーペックスレジェンズ」シーズン7で新たな高みを目指せ。http://x.ea.com/65921

まったく新しい未知の世界が広がる。オリンパスはこれまで以上の危険をはらみ、落下の影響はこれまでの比ではない。新レジェンドのホライゾンはその重大性を認識し、重力を熟知する存在。他のレジェンドが望むと望まざるに関わらず、空中へと巻き上げてしまう。オリンパスでは飛行型ビークル「トライデント」に乗り込み、バトルパスを手にしてランクシリーズの上位を目指そう。新登場の「クラブ」機能を使って自身のコミュニティを作ることも可能だ。11月4日、シーズン7で高みを目指せ。

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One、PS4、Steam、Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

localizations.ko.description:
Apex 레전드 시즌 7에서 새로운 천공의 도시 올림푸스로 떠오르십시오.  http://x.ea.com/65921

완전히 새로운 세계를 탐험하십시오. 높은 고도의 올림푸스에서는 위험도 더 커집니다. 신규 레전드 호라이즌은 중력만큼이나 중대한 상황을 이해하며, 다른 레전드를 높이 띄워 줍니다. 원하지 않더라도 말이죠. 올림푸스의 부양 트라이던트 차량에 타보고, 최신 배틀 패스를 손에 넣고 랭크의 최상위로 뛰어오르며 클럽을 만들어 공동체를 운영하십시오. 11월 4일 시즌7으로 게임의 수준을 한층 더 높이십시오.

Apex 레전드™는 전설적인 캐릭터들이 영광과 명성, 부를 쟁취하기 위해 프런티어의 변경에서 치열한 전투를 벌이는 부분 유료 배틀 로얄 게임입니다. Xbox One, PlayStation 4 및 PC용 Steam 및 Origin에서 Apex 레전드를 무료 플레이하십시오. 

TITLE: Apex 레전드 시즌 7 – 어센션 출시 트레일러


Apex 레전드 시즌 7 – 어센션의 더 자세한 정보: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
YouTube 채널: http://x.ea.com/56710
Twitter 팔로우: https://twitter.com/playapex
Instagram 팔로우: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/

#호라이즌소개 #Apex시즌7 #Apex시즌7 #Apex레전드
localizations.ar.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – إعلان طرح Ascension
localizations.ar.description:
ارتق إلى مستويات جديدة في الموسم 7 من Apex Legends في مدينة Olympus الطافية.  http://x.ea.com/65921

هنالك عالم جديد بالكامل في انتظارك لكي تستكشفه. إن المخاطر عالية والإخفاقات أشد فتكًا في Olympus. الأسطورة الجديدة Horizon تعي خطورة الموقف, وسوف تحرص على تقديم المساعدة للجميع, سواء أرادوا ذلك أم لا. بالإضافة إلى ذلك, استخدم مركبات Trident الطافية في Olympus, واحصل على أحدث Battle Pass, واصعد إلى قمة Ranked, وقم ببناء مجتمعك باستخدام الأندية. ارفع من مستوى لعبك عندما يتم إصدار الموسم 7 في 4 نوفمبر.

Apex Legends™‎ هي لعبة معارك مجانية حيث تتقاتل شخصيات أسطورية بحثًا عن المجد والشهرة والثروة على أطراف Frontier. العب مجانًا الآن على Xbox One, وPS4, وSteam, وOrigin للكمبيوتر الشخصي. 

العنوان: Apex Legends Season 7 – إعلان طرح Ascension


تعرّف على المزيد عن الموسم 7 من Apex Legends – Ascension: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
راجع قناة YouTube الخاصة بنا: http://x.ea.com/56710.
تابعنا علىTwitter‏: https://twitter.com/playapex.
تابعنا على Instagram‏: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

‎#MeetHorizon #ApexSeason7 #ApexSeason7 #ApexLegends
localizations.fi.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascensionin julkaisutraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Nouse uusiin korkeuksiin Apex Legendsin 7. kaudella Olympuksen leijuvassa kaupungissa. http://x.ea.com/65921

Kokonainen uusi maailma odottaa tutkimista. Olympuksessa panokset ovat kovemmat ja pudotukset vaarallisempia kuin koskaan. Uusi legenda Horizon ymmärtää tilanteen vakavuuden, ja hän on valmis antamaan muille legendoille kyytiä – halusivatpa he sitä tai eivät. Hyppää Olympuksen leijuviin Trident-autoihin, nappaa uusin Battle Pass, nouse tilastojen huipulle ja kokoa oma yhteisö Klubien avulla. Näytä taitosi, kun Season 7 käynnistyy 4. marraskuuta.

Apex Legends™ on ilmainen battle royale -peli, jossa legendaariset hahmot taistelevat maineesta, kunniasta ja mammonasta Frontierin laitamilla. Pelaa nyt ilmaiseksi Xbox Onella, PS4-järjestelmällä ja PC:llä Steamin ja Originin kautta. 

TITLE: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascensionin julkaisutraileri


Lue lisää Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascensionista: http://x.ea.com/65921

Seuraa meitä Instagramissa: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

localizations.ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер к выходу сезона 7 «Вознесение»
localizations.ru.description:
Достигните новых высот в сезоне 7 Apex Legends в парящем городе Олимпе.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Вашему взору открывается новый мир. На Олимпе взлеты опаснее, а падения — болезненнее. Новая легенда Хорайзон осознает всю силу тяжести положения и готова помочь другим легендам воспарить духом, хотят они того или нет. Запрыгивайте в летающий транспорт «Трезубец», берите новый боевой пропуск, устремляйтесь к вершинам рейтингового режима и создавайте свое сообщество с помощью клубов. Поднимитесь на новый уровень с началом сезона 7 уже 4 ноября.

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на Xbox One, PS4, в Steam и Origin для ПК. 

НАЗВАНИЕ: Apex Legends — трейлер к выходу сезона 7 «Вознесение»

localizations.pt-BR.title: Trailer de Lançamento da Temporada 7 - Ascenção de Apex Legends
localizations.pt-BR.description:
Ascenda a novas alturas na Temporada 7 de Apex Legends  na cidade voadora Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Há um mundo inteiro esperando para ser explorado. As apostas são altas e as quedas são fatais em Olympus. A nova Lenda, Horizon, entende a gravidade da situação, e ela não se importa em dar um impulso a outras Lendas, elas querendo ou não. Além disso, divirta-se com Trident, o veículo voador de Olympus, obtenha o mais novo Passe de Batalha e suba ao topo da Liga, além de construir sua comunidade com Clubes. Melhore seu jogo quando a Temporada 7 for lançada, dia 4 de novembro.

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito de battle royale em que personagens lendários lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nos limites da Fronteira. Jogue Apex Legends de graça agora no Xbox One, PlayStation®4, Steam e Origin para PC.

localizations.nl-NL.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Klim naar nieuwe hoogten tijdens Apex Legends Season 7 in de zwevende stad Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Er wacht een hele nieuwe wereld op verkenning. Op Olympus is de inzet hoger en zijn de vallen dodelijker. De nieuwe Legend Horizon begrijpt de ernst van de situatie, en zal de andere Legends zeker een ""lift"" geven: of ze nu willen of niet. Spring daarnaast op de zwevende Trident-voertuigen van Olympus, pak de nieuwste Battle Pass, klim omhoog naar de top van Ranked en bouw je community op met clubs. Verbeter je spel als Season 7 wordt uitgebracht op 4 november.

Apex Legends™ is een free-to-play battle royale-spel waarin legendarische personages strijden om glorie, roem en fortuin aan de rand van de Frontier. Speel nu gratis op de Xbox One, PS4, Steam en Origin for PC.

localizations.sv.title: Lanseringstrailer för Apex Legends Säsong 7 – Ascension
localizations.sv.description:
Stig upp till nya höjder i Apex Legends Säsong 7 i den svävande staden Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny värld väntar på bli utforskad. Mer står på spel och fallen är dödligare på Olympus. Den nya legendaren Horizon förstår tyngden i situationen och hon kommer säkert ge andra legendarer ett lyft - oavsett om de vill eller inte. Dessutom kan du hoppa på Olympus svävande Trident-fordon, hämta det senaste Battle Passet, klättra upp till toppen på Ranked och bygga en gemenskap med klubbar. Ta ditt spel till nästa nivå när Säsong 7 släpps den 4 november.

Apex Legends™ är ett gratis battle royale-spel där legendariska karaktärer strider för ära, berömmelse och rikedom på gränslandets utkanter. Spela gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam och Origin för PC.

localizations.es-MX.title: Temporada 7 de Apex Legends – Tráiler de lanzamiento de Ascenso
localizations.es-MX.description:
Supera tus límites en la ciudad flotante de Olympus en la temporada 7 de Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un nuevo mundo te espera para ser explorado. En Olympus, las apuestas son más altas y las caídas más letales. Horizon, la nueva leyenda, entiende la gravedad de la situación y está preparada para darle un aventón a las demás leyendas... Lo quieran o no. Súbete a los vehículos flotantes Trident de Olympus, obtén el último Battle Pass, asciende a la cima de la clasificación y crea tu comunidad con los clubes. Mejora tu juego cuando se lance la temporada 7 el 4 de noviembre.

Apex Legends™ es un juego gratuito estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ahora en Xbox One, PS4, Steam y Origin para PC.

localizations.da.title: Apex Legends sæson 7 – lanceringstrailer for Ascension
localizations.da.description:
Nå nye højder i Apex Legends sæson 7 på den svævende by Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden, der bare venter på at blive udforsket. Der er endnu mere på spil og endnu dybere at falde på Olympus. Den nye legende Horizon har forstået situationens alvor, og skal nok give de andre legender et løft – om de vil det eller ej. Desuden kan du hoppe på Olympus' svævende Trident-fartøjer, snuppe det nyeste Battle Pass, nå til tops i Ranked og skabe et fællesskab med klubber. Sæt trumf på dit spil, når sæson 7 udkommer 4. november.

Apex Legends™ er et gratis Battle Royale-spil, hvor legendariske figurer kæmper om hæder, berømmelse og held i grænseområdet. Spil gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam og Origin til pc.

snippet.title: K/DA - MORE ft. Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Ascend the throne. K/DA is back with “MORE,” featuring Madison Beer, SOYEON and MIYEON of (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, and Seraphine.

K/DA is a virtual music supergroup by Ahri, Evelynn, Akali, and Kai’Sa. Look out for their upcoming ALL OUT EP, releasing on November 6, 2020.

Follow @KDA_MUSIC on Twitter and Instagram for updates.

Featured artists: Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine

K/DA
Should we show 'em how we do it everyday
(na na na)
Let's get 'em

Akali that girl
Kali go grr

Kali got a job
Kali go to work
뜨거워 언제나
Don’t get burnt
넘쳐흘러 more than a buffet
난 죽여 주잖아 like I’m Buffy
누가 감히 on my huffy
거- 문 열지 마 that's a rough day

I’m giving you more
Cause I’m greater than
필요 없는 시험들
답은 이미
But all of my numbers are talking babe
부루마블 mrs 모노폴리
너는 - 종이 돈이 나는 real money
필요 없대 너네들이 많은 돈들
Go get it go get it go get it the mission
눈을 못 떼 모두 그래 너도 그래
Cause I got it different

All I’ll ever know
Is life up on a throne
시작하면 끝을 보는 거야
You want

More
Know I got it
So here you go
You look like you could use some more
Know I got it
And never running low
Yeah I got

More than enough add it up and away
You know I got it like
Bomb bomb Blow your mind
Never giving less and that’s how it’ll stay
You know I got it like
All day, All the time

When I go it’s for gold
Yeah they cool but I’m cold
I don’t fit in the mold
I’m a rebel
I don’t do what you say
Making moves I don't wait
While I smile in your face
I got different DNA

What’s higher than the top
That’s me
Come take a look
Before falling at my feet
조용히 몸을 숙여봐
So take a look
나를 기억해 a queen

Way out
感觉犹如海浪
On the wave now
不断往前遨游
Never weighed down
就是我每天想要的模样
Wow

But I know I know
You want some more
我知道你
什么要求
But I know I know
You want some more
准备好就一起走
Giving it all

localizations.it.description:
Sali sul trono. Le K/DA sono tornate con "MORE", con la collaborazione di Madison Beer, SOYEON e MIYEON delle (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns e Seraphine.

K/DA è un super gruppo musicale virtuale composto da Ahri, Evelynn, Akali, e Kai'Sa. Preparatevi al loro prossimo album, ALL OUT, in uscita il 6 novembre 2020.

Seguite @KDA_MUSIC su Twitter e Instagram per restare aggiornati.

ASCOLTA ORA:

https://ffm.to/kdamore
Spotify: https://ffm.to/kdamore-spotify
Apple Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-applemusic

Deezer: https://ffm.to/kdamore-deezer

K/DA - "MORE"
Con: Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine 
Scritto da: Il team musicale di Riot e Bekuh BOOM
Traduzione in cinese mandarino: Lexie Liu 
Traduzione in coreano: Lydia Paek e Minji Kim

Testo:

K/DA
Should we show 'em how we do it everyday
(na na na)
Let's get 'em

Akali that girl
Kali go grr
Kali don’t stop
Kali don’t skrr
Kali got a job
Kali go to work
뜨거워 언제나
Don’t get burnt
넘쳐흘러 more than a buffet
난 죽여 주잖아 like I’m Buffy
누가 감히 on my huffy
거- 문 열지 마 that's a rough day

I’m giving you more
Cause I’m greater than
필요 없는 시험들
답은 이미
But all of my numbers are talking babe
부루마블 mrs 모노폴리
너는 - 종이 돈이 나는 real money
필요 없대 너네들이 많은 돈들
Go get it go get it go get it the mission
눈을 못 떼 모두 그래 너도 그래
Cause I got it different

All I’ll ever know
Is life up on a throne
시작하면 끝을 보는 거야
You want

More
Know I got it
So here you go
You look like you could use some more
Know I got it
And never running low
Yeah I got

More than enough add it up and away
You know I got it like
Bomb bomb Blow your mind
Never giving less and that’s how it’ll stay
You know I got it like
All day, All the time

When I go it’s for gold
Yeah they cool but I’m cold
I don’t fit in the mold
I’m a rebel
I don’t do what you say
Making moves I don't wait
While I smile in your face
I got different DNA

What’s higher than the top
That’s me
Come take a look
Before falling at my feet
조용히 몸을 숙여봐
So take a look
나를 기억해 a queen

Way out
感觉犹如海浪
On the wave now
不断往前遨游
Never weighed down
就是我每天想要的模样
Wow

But I know I know
You want some more
我知道你
什么要求
But I know I know
You want some more
准备好就一起走
Giving it all

snippet.title: Tamar Braxton Breaks Her Silence Following Suicide Attempt
snippet.description:
Reality TV star and singer Tamar Braxton speaks publicly for the first time after her reported suicide attempt. She details her battle with depression due to her portrayal on reality TV and addresses the allegations of domestic violence with her ex-boyfriend David Adefeso.

From the deeply moving to the purely fun, “Tamron Hall” is a daily destination for all things topical and a platform for viewers to connect with the people who are shaping our world through meaningful, engaging, and entertaining conversations. Broadcast from New York City featuring a dynamic mix of live and taped shows, “Tamron Hall” airs across the country in national syndication.

snippet.title: How AMONG US took over the World (with murder).
snippet.description:
Among Us has recently gone from little known indie game - to worldwide phenomenon in just a few months. From 50 concurrent players to 3 million. While we're all enjoying the entertainment side of the game, I wanted to also take a look at the lessons we can draw from the journey of the developers - InnerSloth, a small team of just three people who, not too long ago, were barely getting by trying to keep the game alive. It's a fascinating case study that I think is worth taking a look at.

------------------------------
➤Follow me on INSTAGRAM:
https://www.instagram.com/andreiterbea/
➤Follow me on TWITTER: https://twitter.com/AndreiTerbea

➤Follow WILFUR on Twitter: https://twitter.com/WilfurTheGoose

https://www.instagram.com/jtefe.ro/

snippet.title: Quando Rondo - Way Up [Official Music Video]
snippet.description:
Quando Rondo - Way Up
Stream/Download 'Diary of a Lost Child': https://quandorondo.lnk.to/DiaryOfALostChild 

Subscribe for more official content from Quando Rondo: https://1633.lnk.to/QuandoRondoSubscribe

Follow Quando Rondo
https://facebook.com/QuandoRondo
https://instagram.com/quando_rondo
https://twitter.com/quando_rondo
https://soundcloud.com/quandorondo

A natural talent, Quando Rondo was once a small child, secretly singing in the bathroom as a 9-year-old boy in Savannah, GA. His natural gravitation towards music lead to him to hip-hop; he began recording his fledgling verses on his cell phone. He quickly gained traction online, racking up millions of views on YouTube.

Fittingly, he titled his 2018 mixtape 'Life B4 Fame' with the hopes that things would change for the better once his career really took off. He was right—within two days, his mixtape had amassed more than one million streams on MyMixtapez. Things will only go up from there, and if the snippets from his forthcoming Rich Homie Quando project are any sign, he’s only only getting better with time.

snippet.title: Why Do Things Keep Evolving Into Crabs?
snippet.description:
Help out Eons and take the PBS Digital Studios annual survey: http://to.pbs.org/2020survey

For some reason, animals keep evolving into things that look like crabs, independently, over and over again. What is it about the crab’s form that makes it so evolutionarily successful that non-crabs are apparently jealous of it? 

Thanks to Franz Anthony for all of the ancient crab (and "crab") illustrations featured throughout this episode! http://franzanth.com/ And special thanks to Dr. Jo Wolfe, Dr. Javier Luque, and Dr. Katie Collins for assisting Franz with research for those illustrations. 

And thank you to Dr. Rodney Feldmann for providing a photo of the Paralomis debodeorum fossil!

Produced in collaboration with PBS Digital Studios: http://youtube.com/pbsdigitalstudios

Super special thanks to the following Patreon patrons for helping make Eons possible:
Matt D, Yu Mei, Colleen Troussel, Dan Ritter, Drew Hart, faxo, Gary Walker, Stephanie Tan, Minyuan Li, Ben Cooper, Leonid, Robert Noah, Matt Parker, Heathe Kyle, Yeakley, Jerrit Erickson, Jack Arbuckle, David Sewall, Anton Bryl, MissyElliottSmith, Zachary Spencer, Stefan Weber, Andrey, Ilya Murashov, Larry Wilson, Merri, Snaidman, Marcus Lejon, Robert Arévalo, Todd Dittman, Betsy Radley, Anthony Callaghan, Laura Sanborn, PS, Philip Slingerland, John Vanek, Eric Vonk, Henrik Peteri, Jon Monteiro, James Bording, Miles Chaston, Michael McClellan, Jeff Graham, Maria Humphrey, Daisuke Goto, Hubert Rady, Gregory Kintz, Tyson, Chandler Bass, Joao, Ascensao, Tsee Lee, Robert Hill, and Frida Coffey.

snippet.title: President Donald Trump: The 60 Minutes 2020 Election Interview
snippet.description:
In an interview that's made headlines this week, Lesley Stahl presses President Trump on once-again rising coronavirus cases and what his priorities would be if re-elected. Stahl also speaks with Mr. Trump's running mate, Vice President Mike Pence. https://cbsn.ws/3mhiSZK

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu
Watch Full Episodes of 60 Minutes HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Qkjo1F
Get more 60 Minutes from 60 Minutes: Overtime HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1KG3sdr
Relive past episodes and interviews with 60 Minutes Rewind HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1PlZiGI
Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Manchester United vs. RB Leipzig: Extended Highlights | UCL on CBS Sports
snippet.description:
Smart Greenwood got the scoring going for Manchester United with a goal in the 21’. Paul Pogba slipped the ball in to Greenwood in the left channel and the United youngster used one touch and finished low to give Man. U the lead to start the game. 

Manchester United really turned up the pressure in the second half behind Marcus Rashford’s quick brace. Rashford cut behind the Leipzig back line with a timely run for his first goal in the 74’ then just four minutes later he found the back of the net. The match went from a tightly contested 1-0 game to a big 3-0 Manchester United win in a matter of four minutes.

Man. U would go on to add a goal in the 87’ from Anthony Martial by way of penalty and Marcus Rashford would complete his hat trick in the 90’+2 to finish the game with a 5-0 dominating win. 
Stream every UEFA Champions League match live on CBS All Access:
http://bit.ly/ucloncbssports

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Snowy Escape: Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The wonders of Mt. Komorebi await in The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack!* Slow down to take it all in, or rush into the adventure of a lifetime. Learn more here: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Get an insider’s point-of-view from a Mt. Komorebi local as she takes you through her world. Learn to appreciate the culture of this mountain town as well as its more well-known features, like its famous snow activities and serene hot springs. Have you booked your trip yet? 

Available November 13, 2020, on PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, and PlayStation®4.

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Preorder now: http://x.ea.com/65834.

Se Komorebifjellet fra innsiden ved å være med en lokal sim som viser deg rundt i verdenen. Lær deg å sette pris på kulturen i denne fjellandsbyen, samt de velkjente tilbudene som finnes her, som berømte vinteraktiviteter og fredelige varme kilder. Har du bestilt din tur? 

Ute 13. november 2020 på PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One og PlayStation®4.

Les mer om denne utvidelsespakken: http://x.ea.com/65833 
Forhåndsbestill nå: http://x.ea.com/65834 

*KREVER AT DU HAR THE SIMS 4-GRUNNSPILLET (SELGES SEPARAT) OG ALLE SPILLOPPDATERINGENE. FOR PC: SJEKK MINSTE SYSTEMKRAV FOR DENNE PAKKEN.
localizations.it.title: The Sims 4 Oasi Innevata: trailer di gioco ufficiale
localizations.it.description:
Le meraviglie del monte Komorebi ti attendono in The Sims™ 4 Oasi Innevata Expansion Pack!* Rallenta per assaporare ogni istante o accelera verso l'avventura della tua vita! Scopri i dettagli qui: http://x.ea.com/65833

Lasciati consigliare da un'abitante del monte Komorebi che ti farà da guida attraverso lo scenario. Impara ad apprezzare la cultura della cittadina di montagna oltre alle sue qualità più note, come le rinomate attività invernali e le tranquille sorgenti termali. Hai già prenotato il tuo viaggio? 

Disponibile il 13 novembre 2020 per PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One e PlayStation®4.

Scopri i dettagli dell'Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833 
Prenota subito: http://x.ea.com/65834 

*RICHIEDE THE SIMS 4 (VENDUTO SEPARATAMENTE) E TUTTI GLI AGGIORNAMENTI DEL GIOCO. PER PC, LEGGI I REQUISITI MINIMI DI SISTEMA DEL PACCHETTO.
localizations.pl.title: The Sims 4 Śnieżna eskapada: oficjalny zwiastun rozgrywki
localizations.pl.description:
Cudowna góra Komorebi czeka na Ciebie w The Sims™ 4 Śnieżna eskapada Dodatek*! Zwolnij tempo i odpręż się lub ruszaj na przygodę życia. Dowiedz się więcej: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Spójrz na okolicę oczami miejscowej, która oprowadza Cię po górze Komorebi. Poznaj kulturę tego górskiego miasteczka oraz jego słynne atrakcje, takie jak sporty zimowe i odprężające gorące źródła. Masz już bilety na wypad? 

13 listopada 2020 r. premiera wersji na komputery PC/Mac, Steam oraz Xbox One i PlayStation®4.

Więcej informacji na temat tego Dodatku na stronie: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Zamów w przedsprzedaży: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*WYMAGA GRY THE SIMS 4 (SPRZEDAWANEJ ODDZIELNIE) I WSZYSTKICH JEJ AKTUALIZACJI. SPRAWDŹ MINIMALNE WYMAGANIA SYSTEMOWE TEGO PAKIETU W WERSJI NA PC.
localizations.ja.title: 「The Sims 4 Snowy Escape」: 公式ゲームプレイトレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
「The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack」（※）でコモレビ山の銀世界が待っている！ 和のくつろぎに身を任せ、スリル満点のアドベンチャーに挑戦しよう。詳細はこちら: http://x.ea.com/65833

コモレビ山の住人が彼女の住む素敵な町をご紹介します！山に抱かれた街の人気のスノースポーツやくつろぎの温泉などの有名スポットから文化までをご覧ください。もう旅のご予約はお済みですか？

PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One、PlayStation®4で2020年11月13日発売。

この拡張パックの詳細はこちら: http://x.ea.com/65833.
いますぐ予約: http://x.ea.com/65834

（※）プレイには「The Sims 4」ゲーム本編（別売）と、すべてのゲームアップデートの適用が必要です。PC版は本パックの必要動作環境をご確認ください。
localizations.es-ES.title: Los Sims 4 Escapada en la Nieve: tráiler oficial de juego
localizations.es-ES.description:
¡Descubre las maravillas del monte Komorebi en Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* Tómate tu tiempo para disfrutarlo todo o embárcate en la aventura de tu vida sin perder un instante. Obtén más información aquí: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Obtén el punto de vista de una lugareña del monte Komorebi mientras te enseña su mundo. Aprende a apreciar la cultura de esta ciudad de montaña y sus características más conocidas, como sus famosas actividades en la nieve y sus relajantes aguas termales. ¿Has reservado ya tu viaje? 

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Descubre más cosas sobre este pack de expansión: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Resérvalo ya: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*SE NECESITA LOS SIMS 4 (SE VENDE POR SEPARADO) CON TODAS SUS ACTUALIZACIONES. CONSULTA LOS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DEL SISTEMA DEL PACK PARA PC.
localizations.ko.title: The Sims 4 겨울이야기: 공식 게임 플레이 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
The Sims™ 4 겨울이야기 확장팩*에 코모레비산이 선사하는 경이로운 체험이 기다립니다! 느림의 미학으로 모든 경이로움을 느껴보고, 인생의 모험을 향해 돌진하세요! 여기서 자세히 알아보세요: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/65833.

코모레비산 토박이의 관점에서 코모레비산을 체험하세요. 유명한 설원 스포츠와 온천 같은 잘 알려진 자랑거리 외에도 이 산악 마을의 문화를 느낄 수있는 방법을 배워보세요. 아직 여행을 예약하지 않으셨습니까? 

2020년 11월 13일 PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, PlayStation®4용으로 출시됩니다.

이 확장팩에 관해 자세히 알아보기: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/65833. 
지금 예약 구매: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/65834. 

*플레이하려면 THE SIMS 4 게임 (별매) 및 모든 게임 업데이트가 필요합니다. 이 팩의 PC 최소 사양을 확인하세요.
localizations.fi.title: The Sims 4 Lumisten vuorten maa: virallinen pelitraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Komorebi-vuoren ihmeet odottavat The Sims™ 4 Lumisten vuorten maa Expansion Packissä!* Hidasta tahtia ja nauti maisemista ja kiidä elämäsi seikkailuun. Lue lisää täältä: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Sisäpiiriläisen näkökulma! Komorebi-vuoren paikallinen asukas vie sinut kierrokselle maailmaansa. Tutustu vuorikylän kulttuuriin ja sen tunnetuimpiin piirteisiin, kuten kuuluisiin talvihupeihin ja rentouttaviin kuumiin lähteisiin. Joko olet varannut matkasi? 

Saatavilla 13. marraskuuta 2020 PC:llä/Macillä, Steam-palvelussa, Xbox Onella ja PlayStation®4-järjestelmällä.

Lue lisää tästä Expansion Packistä: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Ennakkotilaa nyt: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*PELAAMISEEN TARVITAAN THE SIMS 4 -PELI (MYYDÄÄN ERIKSEEN) JA KAIKKI PELIPÄIVITYKSET. LUE PAKETIN PC-JÄRJESTELMÄVAATIMUKSET.
localizations.ru.title: Официальный трейлер игрового процесса «The Sims 4 Снежные просторы»
localizations.ru.description:
Чудеса горы Комореби ждут вас в «The Sims™ 4 Снежные просторы Дополнение»!* Притормозите, чтобы впитать всю красоту, или ускорьтесь — навстречу приключениям. Подробнее: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Получите информацию о горе Комореби от местной жительницы, которая покажет вам свой мир. Научитесь ценить культуру этого горного городка и посетите его достопримечательности — популярные лыжные склоны и безмятежные горячие источники. Вы уже готовы готовы ехать? 

С 13 ноября 2020 года на ПК/Mac, Steam, Xbox One и PlayStation®4.

Подробнее про дополнение: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Оформите предзаказ: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

* ДЛЯ ИГРЫ ТРЕБУЕТСЯ НАЛИЧИЕ THE SIMS 4 (ПРОДАЕТСЯ ОТДЕЛЬНО) И ВСЕХ ОБНОВЛЕНИЙ. СМ. МИНИМАЛЬНЫЕ СИСТЕМНЫЕ ТРЕБОВАНИЯ ДЛЯ НАБОРА НА ПК.
localizations.pt-BR.title: The Sims 4 Diversão na Neve: Trailer Oficial de Jogabilidade
localizations.pt-BR.description:
As maravilhas do Monte Komorebi esperam por você no The Sims™ 4 Pacote de Expansão Diversão na Neve!* Relaxe e aprecie as paisagens ou viva a maior aventura da sua vida. Saiba mais aqui: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Veja o Monte Komorebi pelos olhos de uma habitante local, que mostrará seu mundo a você. Aprenda a apreciar a cultura desta cidade na montanha e suas características mais conhecidas, como as famosas atividades na neve e a tranquila fonte termal. Você já agendou sua viagem? 

Disponível em 13 de novembro de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One e PlayStation®4.

Saiba mais sobre este Pacote de Expansão: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Reserve agora: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*REQUER O JOGO THE SIMS 4 (VENDIDO SEPARADAMENTE) E TODAS AS ATUALIZAÇÕES. PARA PC, VERIFIQUE OS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DE SISTEMA DESTE PACOTE.
localizations.sv.title: The Sims 4 Snöiga bergen: Officiell speltrailer
localizations.sv.description:
Mt. Komorebis under väntar på dig i The Sims™ 4 Snöiga bergen Expansion Pack!* Varva ner och insup alltihop, eller storma in i ditt livs äventyr. Läs mer här: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Få en insiderblick via en av Mt. Komorebia lokala invånare och låt henne guida dig runt i sin värld. Lär dig att uppskatta bergsstadens kultur och dess välkända sevärdheter, som de berömda snöaktiviteterna och de stillsamma varma källorna. Har du bokat din resa än? 

Släpps 13 november 2020 till PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One och PlayStation®4.

Läs mer om detta Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Förboka nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*KRÄVER THE SIMS 4 (SÄLJS SEPARAT) OCH ALLA SPELUPPDATERINGAR. FÖR PC, SE MINIMISYSTEMKRAVEN FÖR DETTA PACK.
localizations.es-MX.title: Los Sims 4 Escapada en la Nieve: tráiler de jugabilidad oficial
localizations.es-MX.description:
¡Las maravillas del monte Komorebi te aguardan en Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* No tengas prisa por descubrirlo todo o embárcate a toda velocidad en la aventura de tu vida. Descubre más aquí: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Ponte en la piel de los habitantes del monte Komorebi con una lugareña que te enseñará su mundo. Aprende a apreciar la cultura de esta ciudad montañosa y sus características más conocidas, como sus famosas actividades en la nieve y las aguas termales serenas. ¿Ya hiciste tu reserva? 

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 en PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Descubre más sobre este Pack de Expansión: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Resérvalo ahora: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*SE REQUIERE LOS SIMS 4 (SE VENDE POR SEPARADO) Y TODAS LAS ACTUALIZACIONES DEL JUEGO. CONSULTA LOS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DEL SISTEMA PARA EL PACK EN PC.
localizations.da.title: The Sims 4 Snedrømme: Officiel spiltrailer
localizations.da.description:
Oplev Komorebi-bjergets vidundere i The Sims™ 4 Snedrømme Expansion Pack!* Sæt tempoet ned for at nyde det hele, eller kast dig ud i dit livs vildeste eventyr. Se mere her: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Få lidt insiderviden fra en af de lokale på Komorebi-bjerget, mens hun viser dig rundt i hendes verden. Lær om kulturen i denne flotte bjergby, og hør mere om de berømte sneaktiviteter og beroligende varme kilder. Har du husket at booke din rejse? 

Udkommer d. 13. november 2020 på pc/Mac, Steam, Xbox One og PlayStation®4.

Få mere at vide om denne Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Forudbestil nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*KRÆVER THE SIMS 4 (SÆLGES SEPARAT) SAMT ALLE SPILOPDATERINGER. SE MINIMUMSKRAV FOR DENNE PAKKE TIL PC.
localizations.cs.title: The Sims 4 Život na horách – oficiální upoutávka se záběry z hraní
localizations.cs.description:
V rozšíření The Sims™ 4 Život na horách na vás čekají všechny krásy hory Komorebi!* Trochu zpomalte a v klidu je všechny vstřebejte, nebo se po hlavě vrhněte za svým životním dobrodružstvím. Více informací najdete tady: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Nechte se světem provést jednou z místních obyvatelek hory Komorebi a získejte tak informace přímo od zdroje. Naučte se vychutnávat si kulturu tohoto horského městečka a také jeho známější přednosti, jako jsou slavné zimní sporty a poklidné horké prameny. Už jste si zamluvili svůj život na horách? 

K dostání od 13. listopadu 2020 pro PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One a PlayStation®4.

Více informací o tomto rozšíření najdete na: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Předobjednávejte na: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*VYŽADUJE ZÁKLADNÍ HRU THE SIMS 4 (V PRODEJI SAMOSTATNĚ) A VŠECHNY HERNÍ AKTUALIZACE. PROHLÉDNĚTE SI MINIMÁLNÍ SYSTÉMOVÉ POŽADAVKY TOHOTO BALÍČKU NA PC.
localizations.zh-TW.title: 《The Sims 4 雪國勝地》：官方遊戲預告片
localizations.zh-TW.description:
木漏隙光山的美景就在《The Sims™ 4 雪國勝地》資料片*中等著你！慢活體驗所有美好，或者快速踏上畢生難忘的冒險。更多詳情請前往：http://x.ea.com/65833。

隨著木漏隙光山的居民介紹自己的世界，獲得內行人才知道的資訊。學會欣賞此山中小鎮的文化，以及其更著名的特色，例如名聞遐邇的雪上活動以及寧靜舒適的溫泉。你已經訂好機票了嗎？

2020 年 11 月 13 日將於 PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One、和 PlayStation®4 上推出。

更多詳情請前往：http://x.ea.com/65833。
立即預購：http://x.ea.com/65834。

*需有《THE SIMS 4》主遊戲（另售）與所有遊戲更新。PC 版請參閱此資料片的最低系統需求。
localizations.zh-CN.title: 《The Sims 4 雪境仙踪》：官方游戏预告片
localizations.zh-CN.description:
树影斑驳山的奇景等您来探索，尽在《The Sims™ 4 雪境仙踪》资料片！*品味慢生活的所有美好，或一头扎进前所未有的冒险。更多信息请访问：http://x.ea.com/65833。

随着树影斑驳山的居民介绍自己的世界，获得内部人士才知道的信息。学习欣赏这个山间小镇的文化和著名特色，例如闻名遐迩的雪上活动和幽静安谧的温泉。你已经订好机票了吗？

即将于 2020 年 11 月 13 日登陆 PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One 和 PlayStation®4。

了解更多有关此资料片的信息，请访问：http://x.ea.com/65833。
立即预购：http://x.ea.com/65834。

*需搭配《The Sims 4》（另售）并安装所有游戏更新。PC平台请参阅此资料片的最低系统要求。

snippet.title: Saved by the Bell | Official Trailer | Peacock
snippet.description:
Saved by the Bell is streaming November 25th on Peacock. https://www.peacocktv.com/saved-by-the-bell?cid=20201201originalssbtbownsocial262&utm_campaign=20201201originalssbtb&utm_source=yt&utm_medium=own&utm_content=sbtboriginal&utm_term=peacocktv

The highly anticipated reimagining of SAVED BY THE BELL will premiere on Wednesday, Nov. 25 on Peacock. In the new series, when California governor Zack Morris gets into hot water for closing too many underfunded high schools, he proposes they send the affected students to the most well-funded schools in the state – including Bayside High. The influx of new students gives the privileged Bayside kids (who never have a problem that can't be solved in twenty-two minutes) a much-needed dose of reality. Elizabeth Berkley Lauren and Mario Lopez star in the new SAVED BY THE BELL series, reprising their roles as Jessie Spano and A.C. Slater. John Michael Higgins also stars as Principal Toddman alongside the new class featuring Belmont Cameli, Dexter Darden, Mitchell Hoog, Alycia Pascual-Peña, Josie Totah and Haskiri Velazquez. Tracey Wigfield serves as writer and executive producer for the series, alongside executive producer Franco Bario. Peter Engel also serves as executive producer. SAVED BY THE BELL is produced by Universal Television, a division of Universal Studio Group.

snippet.title: Brandy, Erykah Badu, Teyana Taylor & H.E.R. Represent In Their 2020 Cypher | Hip Hop Awards 20
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Geoengineering: A Horrible Idea We Might Have to Do
snippet.description:
To support Kurzgesagt and learn more about Brilliant, go to https://www.brilliant.org/nutshell and sign up for free. The first 200 people that go to that link will get 20% off the annual Premium subscription.
Thanks to our friends from Brilliant for supporting this channel.

Sources & further reading: 
https://sites.google.com/view/sourcesgeoengineering
 
By the end of the 21st century, humanity is becoming desperate. Decades of heatwaves and droughts have led to unusually  poor harvests, while the warming oceans yield fewer fish each year. In the tropical zones, millions suffer from famine and resource wars have made millions more flee to the north. As things quickly get worse, in an act of desperation, the world's governments decide to enact an emergency plan...
It is far from certain that a grim scenario like this will play out. But the failure of world leaders  to effectively address climate change, makes it far from impossible. 
So in the near future it might become necessary to try something radical to slow down rapid climate change: Geoengineering. Interventions so massive in scale that they might undo centuries of human behavior. Or make everything much worse.
What is geoengineering, is it really an option and what if it goes wrong?

snippet.title: Joe Biden: The 60 Minutes 2020 Election Interview
snippet.description:
The former vice president talks with Norah O'Donnell about the pandemic, taxes, the Supreme Court, and the "stark" differences between himself and President Trump. O'Donnell also speaks with Mr. Biden's running mate, California Senator Kamala Harris. https://cbsn.ws/3mhiSZK

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu
Watch Full Episodes of 60 Minutes HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Qkjo1F
Get more 60 Minutes from 60 Minutes: Overtime HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1KG3sdr
Relive past episodes and interviews with 60 Minutes Rewind HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1PlZiGI
Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Binging with Babish: The Broodwich from Aqua Teen Hunger Force
snippet.description:

snippet.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise to new heights in Apex Legends Season 7 on the floating city of Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

There’s a whole new world waiting to be explored. The stakes are higher and the falls are deadlier on Olympus. New Legend Horizon understands the gravity of the situation, and she’s sure to give the other Legends a lift -- whether they want it or not. Plus hop on Olympus’s floating Trident vehicles, grab the latest Battle Pass, ascend to the top of Ranked, and build your community with Clubs. Up your game when Season 7 releases on November 4.

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. And play on Steam when Season 7 launches on November 4 !  

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#MeetHorizon #ApexSeason7 #ApexSeason7 #ApexLegends 

Song Credits:
“Ain’t Our Time To Die (Champions of Justice Remix)”
Performed by DOROTHY

localizations.de-DE.title: Apex Legends Saison 7 – Aufstieg-Launch-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Starte deinen Höhenflug in Apex Legends Saison 7 auf der schwebenden Stadt Olympus  http://x.ea.com/65921

Erkunde eine völlig neue Welt. Auf Olympus ist der Einsatz höher und jeder Sturz noch tödlicher. Die neue Legende, Horizon, weiß um den Ernst der Lage und hilft den anderen Legenden auf die Sprünge – ob sie wollen oder nicht. Drehe auf Olympus außerdem eine Runde mit den schwebenden Tridents, hol dir den neuesten Battle Pass, klettere an die Spitze der Rangliste und baue mit Clubs deine eigene Community auf. Bringe dein Spiel voran, wenn Saison 7 am 5. November erscheint.

Apex Legends™ ist ein Free-to-Play-Battle-Royale-Spiel, bei dem legendäre Charaktere am Rande des Grenzlands um Ruhm und Reichtum kämpfen. Jetzt kostenlos auf Xbox One, PS4 sowie Steam und Origin für PC spielen.

localizations.pt-PT.description:
Sobe a novas alturas na cidade flutuante de Olympus com a Temporada 7 de Apex Legends  http://x.ea.com/65921

Há um mundo à espera de ser explorado. Em Olympus, o risco é grande e as quedas são ainda maiores. Podes ainda sentar-te ao volante dos veículos flutuantes Trident, agarrar o mais recente Battle Pass, atingir o topo da classificação e contribuir para a comunidade com os Clubs. Melhora o teu jogo a 4 de novembro com o arranque da Temporada 7.

Découvrez le Trident, un aéroglisseur qui vous aidera à traverser Olympus à toute vitesse, obtenez le nouveau Passe de combat, progressez dans les ligues classées et développez votre communauté grâce au système de clubs. Préparez-vous pour la saison 7, qui débutera le 4 novembre.

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation 4, Xbox One et Steam ou Origin pour PC.

localizations.ja.description:

まったく新しい未知の世界が広がる。オリンパスはこれまで以上の危険をはらみ、落下の影響はこれまでの比ではない。新レジェンドのホライゾンはその重大性を認識し、重力を熟知する存在。他のレジェンドが望むと望まざるに関わらず、空中へと巻き上げてしまう。オリンパスでは飛行型ビークル「トライデント」に乗り込み、バトルパスを手にしてランクシリーズの上位を目指そう。新登場の「クラブ」機能を使って自身のコミュニティを作ることも可能だ。11月4日、シーズン7で高みを目指せ。

localizations.es-MX.description:
Supera tus límites en la ciudad flotante de Olympus en la temporada 7 de Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un nuevo mundo te espera para ser explorado. En Olympus, las apuestas son más altas y las caídas más letales. Horizon, la nueva leyenda, entiende la gravedad de la situación y está preparada para darle un aventón a las demás leyendas... Lo quieran o no. Súbete a los vehículos flotantes Trident de Olympus, obtén el último Battle Pass, asciende a la cima de la clasificación y crea tu comunidad con los clubes. Mejora tu juego cuando se lance la temporada 7 el 4 de noviembre.

Apex Legends™ es un juego gratuito estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ahora en Xbox One, PS4, Steam y Origin para PC. 

TÍTULO: Temporada 7 de Apex Legends – Tráiler de lanzamiento de Ascenso


Descubre más sobre la temporada 7 de Apex Legends – Ascenso: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
Checa nuestro canal de YouTube: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Síguenos en Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Síguenos en Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#MeetHorizon #ApexSeason7 #ApexSeason7 #ApexLegends
localizations.da.title: Apex Legends sæson 7 – lanceringstrailer for Ascension
localizations.da.description:
Nå nye højder i Apex Legends sæson 7 på den svævende by Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden, der bare venter på at blive udforsket. Der er endnu mere på spil og endnu dybere at falde på Olympus. Den nye legende Horizon har forstået situationens alvor, og skal nok give de andre legender et løft – om de vil det eller ej. Desuden kan du hoppe på Olympus' svævende Trident-fartøjer, snuppe det nyeste Battle Pass, nå til tops i Ranked og skabe et fællesskab med klubber. Sæt trumf på dit spil, når sæson 7 udkommer 4. november.

Apex Legends™ er et gratis Battle Royale-spil, hvor legendariske figurer kæmper om hæder, berømmelse og held i grænseområdet. Spil gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam og Origin til pc. 

TITEL: Apex Legends sæson 7 – lanceringstrailer for Ascension


Få mere at vide om Apex Legends sæson 7 – Ascension: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
Se vores YouTube-kanal: http://x.ea.com/56710.

Følg os på Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

snippet.title: How AMONG US took over the World (with murder).
snippet.description:
Among Us has recently gone from little known indie game - to worldwide phenomenon in just a few months. From 50 concurrent players to 3 million. While we're all enjoying the entertainment side of the game, I wanted to also take a look at the lessons we can draw from the journey of the developers - InnerSloth, a small team of just three people who, not too long ago, were barely getting by trying to keep the game alive. It's a fascinating case study that I think is worth taking a look at.

------------------------------

https://www.instagram.com/andreiterbea/
➤Follow me on TWITTER: https://twitter.com/AndreiTerbea

------------------------------

Stefan Popa - Assistant Animator
https://www.instagram.com/jtefe.ro/

Nicoleta Toader - Producer


------------------------------

http://youtube.com/joakimkarud

snippet.title: The Sims 4 Snowy Escape: Official Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The wonders of Mt. Komorebi await in The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack!* Slow down to take it all in, or rush into the adventure of a lifetime. Learn more here: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Get an insider’s point-of-view from a Mt. Komorebi local as she takes you through her world. Learn to appreciate the culture of this mountain town as well as its more well-known features, like its famous snow activities and serene hot springs. Have you booked your trip yet? 

Available November 13, 2020, on PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, and PlayStation®4.

Learn more about this Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Preorder now: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

#Sims4SnowyEscape #TheSims4 #SnowyEscape #TheSims

*REQUIRES THE SIMS 4 (SOLD SEPARATELY) AND ALL GAME UPDATES. FOR PC, SEE MINIMUM SYSTEM REQUIREMENTS FOR THE PACK.

localizations.de-DE.title: Die Sims 4 Ab ins Schneeparadies: Offizieller Gameplay-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Die Wunder von Mt. Komorebi warten auf dich im Die Sims™ 4 Ab ins Schneeparadies-Erweiterungspack!* Schalte einen Gang runter, um alle Eindrücke aufzunehmen, oder stürze dich in das Abenteuer deines Lebens. Weitere Informationen: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Eine Einheimische aus Mt. Komorebi erklärt dir ihre Welt. Erfahre mehr über die Kultur, berühmten Wintersportmöglichkeiten und friedvollen heißen Quellen der Bergstadt. Hast du deinen Aufenthalt schon gebucht? 

Ab 13. November 2020 für PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One und PlayStation®4 erhältlich.

Erfahre mehr über dieses Erweiterungspack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Jetzt vorbestellen: http://x.ea.com/65834 

*BENÖTIGT DIE SIMS 4 (SEPARATER VERKAUF) UND ALLE SPIELUPDATES. SIEH DIR DIE PC-MINDESTANFORDERUNGEN FÜR DIESES PACK AN.
localizations.pt-PT.title: The Sims 4 Snowy Escape: Trailer oficial de jogabilidade
localizations.pt-PT.description:
As maravilhas de Mt. Komorebi esperam por ti em The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack!* Relaxa e aprecia tudo bem, ou salta para a aventura da tua vida. Descobre mais aqui: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Descobre a opinião de um local de Mt. Komorebi à medida que ela te guia pelo seu mundo. Aprende a apreciar a cultura desta cidade de montanha assim como as suas características mais conhecidas como as suas famosas atividades na neve e serenas fontes termais. Já reservaste a tua viagem? 

Disponível 13 de Novembro de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One e PlayStation®4.

Descobre mais sobre este Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Reserva já: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*REQUER THE SIMS 4 (VENDIDO EM SEPARADO) E DE TODAS AS ATUALIZAÇÕES. PARA PC, CONSULTA OS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DE SISTEMA PARA ESTE PACK.
localizations.fr-FR.title: Les Sims 4 Escapade enneigée : bande-annonce officielle du gameplay
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Les merveilles de Mont Komorebi vous attendent dans le pack d'extension Les Sims™ 4 Escapade enneigée !* Ralentissez pour profiter pleinement de chaque instant, ou lancez-vous dans la plus grande aventure de votre vie. Plus d'informations ici : http://x.ea.com/65833.

Obtenez le point de vue d'initiée d'une habitante de Mont Komorebi qui vous fait visiter son univers. Apprenez à apprécier la culture de cette ville de montagne et ses particularités les plus réputées, comme ses célèbres sports d'hiver et ses sources chaudes paisibles. Avez-vous déjà réservé votre séjour ? 

Disponible le 13 novembre 2020 sur PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One et PlayStation®4.

Plus d'informations sur ce pack d'extension : http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Précommandez dès maintenant : http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*NÉCESSITE LE JEU LES SIMS 4 (VENDU SÉPARÉMENT) ET TOUTES SES MISES À JOUR. SI VOUS JOUEZ SUR PC, CONSULTEZ LA CONFIGURATION MINIMALE REQUISE POUR CE PACK.
localizations.no.title: The Sims 4 Snøparadis: Spillopplevelsestrailer
localizations.no.description:
Komorebifjellets underverker venter på deg i The Sims™ 4 Snøparadis Utvidelsespakke!* Ro ned og ta inn alle inntrykk eller søk eventyrene du alltid har drømt om. Finn ut mer her: http://x.ea.com/65833

Se Komorebifjellet fra innsiden ved å være med en lokal sim som viser deg rundt i verdenen. Lær deg å sette pris på kulturen i denne fjellandsbyen, samt de velkjente tilbudene som finnes her, som berømte vinteraktiviteter og fredelige varme kilder. Har du bestilt din tur? 

Ute 13. november 2020 på PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One og PlayStation®4.

Les mer om denne utvidelsespakken: http://x.ea.com/65833 
Forhåndsbestill nå: http://x.ea.com/65834 

*KREVER AT DU HAR THE SIMS 4-GRUNNSPILLET (SELGES SEPARAT) OG ALLE SPILLOPPDATERINGENE. FOR PC: SJEKK MINSTE SYSTEMKRAV FOR DENNE PAKKEN.
localizations.it.title: The Sims 4 Oasi Innevata: trailer di gioco ufficiale
localizations.it.description:
Le meraviglie del monte Komorebi ti attendono in The Sims™ 4 Oasi Innevata Expansion Pack!* Rallenta per assaporare ogni istante o accelera verso l'avventura della tua vita! Scopri i dettagli qui: http://x.ea.com/65833

Lasciati consigliare da un'abitante del monte Komorebi che ti farà da guida attraverso lo scenario. Impara ad apprezzare la cultura della cittadina di montagna oltre alle sue qualità più note, come le rinomate attività invernali e le tranquille sorgenti termali. Hai già prenotato il tuo viaggio? 

Disponibile il 13 novembre 2020 per PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One e PlayStation®4.

Scopri i dettagli dell'Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833 
Prenota subito: http://x.ea.com/65834 

*RICHIEDE THE SIMS 4 (VENDUTO SEPARATAMENTE) E TUTTI GLI AGGIORNAMENTI DEL GIOCO. PER PC, LEGGI I REQUISITI MINIMI DI SISTEMA DEL PACCHETTO.
localizations.pl.title: The Sims 4 Śnieżna eskapada: oficjalny zwiastun rozgrywki
localizations.pl.description:
Cudowna góra Komorebi czeka na Ciebie w The Sims™ 4 Śnieżna eskapada Dodatek*! Zwolnij tempo i odpręż się lub ruszaj na przygodę życia. Dowiedz się więcej: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Spójrz na okolicę oczami miejscowej, która oprowadza Cię po górze Komorebi. Poznaj kulturę tego górskiego miasteczka oraz jego słynne atrakcje, takie jak sporty zimowe i odprężające gorące źródła. Masz już bilety na wypad? 

13 listopada 2020 r. premiera wersji na komputery PC/Mac, Steam oraz Xbox One i PlayStation®4.

Więcej informacji na temat tego Dodatku na stronie: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Zamów w przedsprzedaży: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*WYMAGA GRY THE SIMS 4 (SPRZEDAWANEJ ODDZIELNIE) I WSZYSTKICH JEJ AKTUALIZACJI. SPRAWDŹ MINIMALNE WYMAGANIA SYSTEMOWE TEGO PAKIETU W WERSJI NA PC.
localizations.ja.title: 「The Sims 4 Snowy Escape」: 公式ゲームプレイトレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
「The Sims™ 4 Snowy Escape Expansion Pack」（※）でコモレビ山の銀世界が待っている！ 和のくつろぎに身を任せ、スリル満点のアドベンチャーに挑戦しよう。詳細はこちら: http://x.ea.com/65833

コモレビ山の住人が彼女の住む素敵な町をご紹介します！山に抱かれた街の人気のスノースポーツやくつろぎの温泉などの有名スポットから文化までをご覧ください。もう旅のご予約はお済みですか？

PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One、PlayStation®4で2020年11月13日発売。

この拡張パックの詳細はこちら: http://x.ea.com/65833.
いますぐ予約: http://x.ea.com/65834

（※）プレイには「The Sims 4」ゲーム本編（別売）と、すべてのゲームアップデートの適用が必要です。PC版は本パックの必要動作環境をご確認ください。
localizations.es-ES.title: Los Sims 4 Escapada en la Nieve: tráiler oficial de juego
localizations.es-ES.description:
¡Descubre las maravillas del monte Komorebi en Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* Tómate tu tiempo para disfrutarlo todo o embárcate en la aventura de tu vida sin perder un instante. Obtén más información aquí: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Obtén el punto de vista de una lugareña del monte Komorebi mientras te enseña su mundo. Aprende a apreciar la cultura de esta ciudad de montaña y sus características más conocidas, como sus famosas actividades en la nieve y sus relajantes aguas termales. ¿Has reservado ya tu viaje? 

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Descubre más cosas sobre este pack de expansión: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Resérvalo ya: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*SE NECESITA LOS SIMS 4 (SE VENDE POR SEPARADO) CON TODAS SUS ACTUALIZACIONES. CONSULTA LOS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DEL SISTEMA DEL PACK PARA PC.
localizations.ko.title: The Sims 4 겨울이야기: 공식 게임 플레이 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
The Sims™ 4 겨울이야기 확장팩*에 코모레비산이 선사하는 경이로운 체험이 기다립니다! 느림의 미학으로 모든 경이로움을 느껴보고, 인생의 모험을 향해 돌진하세요! 여기서 자세히 알아보세요: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/65833.

코모레비산 토박이의 관점에서 코모레비산을 체험하세요. 유명한 설원 스포츠와 온천 같은 잘 알려진 자랑거리 외에도 이 산악 마을의 문화를 느낄 수있는 방법을 배워보세요. 아직 여행을 예약하지 않으셨습니까? 

2020년 11월 13일 PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, PlayStation®4용으로 출시됩니다.

이 확장팩에 관해 자세히 알아보기: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/65833. 
지금 예약 구매: http://x.ea.com/ko-kr/65834. 

*플레이하려면 THE SIMS 4 게임 (별매) 및 모든 게임 업데이트가 필요합니다. 이 팩의 PC 최소 사양을 확인하세요.
localizations.fi.title: The Sims 4 Lumisten vuorten maa: virallinen pelitraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Komorebi-vuoren ihmeet odottavat The Sims™ 4 Lumisten vuorten maa Expansion Packissä!* Hidasta tahtia ja nauti maisemista ja kiidä elämäsi seikkailuun. Lue lisää täältä: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Sisäpiiriläisen näkökulma! Komorebi-vuoren paikallinen asukas vie sinut kierrokselle maailmaansa. Tutustu vuorikylän kulttuuriin ja sen tunnetuimpiin piirteisiin, kuten kuuluisiin talvihupeihin ja rentouttaviin kuumiin lähteisiin. Joko olet varannut matkasi? 

Saatavilla 13. marraskuuta 2020 PC:llä/Macillä, Steam-palvelussa, Xbox Onella ja PlayStation®4-järjestelmällä.

Lue lisää tästä Expansion Packistä: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Ennakkotilaa nyt: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*PELAAMISEEN TARVITAAN THE SIMS 4 -PELI (MYYDÄÄN ERIKSEEN) JA KAIKKI PELIPÄIVITYKSET. LUE PAKETIN PC-JÄRJESTELMÄVAATIMUKSET.
localizations.ru.title: Официальный трейлер игрового процесса «The Sims 4 Снежные просторы»
localizations.ru.description:
Чудеса горы Комореби ждут вас в «The Sims™ 4 Снежные просторы Дополнение»!* Притормозите, чтобы впитать всю красоту, или ускорьтесь — навстречу приключениям. Подробнее: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Получите информацию о горе Комореби от местной жительницы, которая покажет вам свой мир. Научитесь ценить культуру этого горного городка и посетите его достопримечательности — популярные лыжные склоны и безмятежные горячие источники. Вы уже готовы готовы ехать? 

С 13 ноября 2020 года на ПК/Mac, Steam, Xbox One и PlayStation®4.

Подробнее про дополнение: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Оформите предзаказ: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

* ДЛЯ ИГРЫ ТРЕБУЕТСЯ НАЛИЧИЕ THE SIMS 4 (ПРОДАЕТСЯ ОТДЕЛЬНО) И ВСЕХ ОБНОВЛЕНИЙ. СМ. МИНИМАЛЬНЫЕ СИСТЕМНЫЕ ТРЕБОВАНИЯ ДЛЯ НАБОРА НА ПК.
localizations.pt-BR.title: The Sims 4 Diversão na Neve: Trailer Oficial de Jogabilidade
localizations.pt-BR.description:
As maravilhas do Monte Komorebi esperam por você no The Sims™ 4 Pacote de Expansão Diversão na Neve!* Relaxe e aprecie as paisagens ou viva a maior aventura da sua vida. Saiba mais aqui: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Veja o Monte Komorebi pelos olhos de uma habitante local, que mostrará seu mundo a você. Aprenda a apreciar a cultura desta cidade na montanha e suas características mais conhecidas, como as famosas atividades na neve e a tranquila fonte termal. Você já agendou sua viagem? 

Disponível em 13 de novembro de 2020 para PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One e PlayStation®4.

Saiba mais sobre este Pacote de Expansão: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Reserve agora: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*REQUER O JOGO THE SIMS 4 (VENDIDO SEPARADAMENTE) E TODAS AS ATUALIZAÇÕES. PARA PC, VERIFIQUE OS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DE SISTEMA DESTE PACOTE.
localizations.sv.title: The Sims 4 Snöiga bergen: Officiell speltrailer
localizations.sv.description:
Mt. Komorebis under väntar på dig i The Sims™ 4 Snöiga bergen Expansion Pack!* Varva ner och insup alltihop, eller storma in i ditt livs äventyr. Läs mer här: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Få en insiderblick via en av Mt. Komorebia lokala invånare och låt henne guida dig runt i sin värld. Lär dig att uppskatta bergsstadens kultur och dess välkända sevärdheter, som de berömda snöaktiviteterna och de stillsamma varma källorna. Har du bokat din resa än? 

Släpps 13 november 2020 till PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One och PlayStation®4.

Läs mer om detta Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Förboka nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*KRÄVER THE SIMS 4 (SÄLJS SEPARAT) OCH ALLA SPELUPPDATERINGAR. FÖR PC, SE MINIMISYSTEMKRAVEN FÖR DETTA PACK.
localizations.es-MX.title: Los Sims 4 Escapada en la Nieve: tráiler de jugabilidad oficial
localizations.es-MX.description:
¡Las maravillas del monte Komorebi te aguardan en Los Sims™ 4 Escapada en la Nieve Pack de Expansión!* No tengas prisa por descubrirlo todo o embárcate a toda velocidad en la aventura de tu vida. Descubre más aquí: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Ponte en la piel de los habitantes del monte Komorebi con una lugareña que te enseñará su mundo. Aprende a apreciar la cultura de esta ciudad montañosa y sus características más conocidas, como sus famosas actividades en la nieve y las aguas termales serenas. ¿Ya hiciste tu reserva? 

Disponible el 13 de noviembre de 2020 en PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One y PlayStation®4.

Descubre más sobre este Pack de Expansión: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Resérvalo ahora: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*SE REQUIERE LOS SIMS 4 (SE VENDE POR SEPARADO) Y TODAS LAS ACTUALIZACIONES DEL JUEGO. CONSULTA LOS REQUISITOS MÍNIMOS DEL SISTEMA PARA EL PACK EN PC.
localizations.da.title: The Sims 4 Snedrømme: Officiel spiltrailer
localizations.da.description:
Oplev Komorebi-bjergets vidundere i The Sims™ 4 Snedrømme Expansion Pack!* Sæt tempoet ned for at nyde det hele, eller kast dig ud i dit livs vildeste eventyr. Se mere her: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Få lidt insiderviden fra en af de lokale på Komorebi-bjerget, mens hun viser dig rundt i hendes verden. Lær om kulturen i denne flotte bjergby, og hør mere om de berømte sneaktiviteter og beroligende varme kilder. Har du husket at booke din rejse? 

Udkommer d. 13. november 2020 på pc/Mac, Steam, Xbox One og PlayStation®4.

Få mere at vide om denne Expansion Pack: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Forudbestil nu: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*KRÆVER THE SIMS 4 (SÆLGES SEPARAT) SAMT ALLE SPILOPDATERINGER. SE MINIMUMSKRAV FOR DENNE PAKKE TIL PC.
localizations.cs.title: The Sims 4 Život na horách – oficiální upoutávka se záběry z hraní
localizations.cs.description:
V rozšíření The Sims™ 4 Život na horách na vás čekají všechny krásy hory Komorebi!* Trochu zpomalte a v klidu je všechny vstřebejte, nebo se po hlavě vrhněte za svým životním dobrodružstvím. Více informací najdete tady: http://x.ea.com/65833.

Nechte se světem provést jednou z místních obyvatelek hory Komorebi a získejte tak informace přímo od zdroje. Naučte se vychutnávat si kulturu tohoto horského městečka a také jeho známější přednosti, jako jsou slavné zimní sporty a poklidné horké prameny. Už jste si zamluvili svůj život na horách? 

K dostání od 13. listopadu 2020 pro PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One a PlayStation®4.

Více informací o tomto rozšíření najdete na: http://x.ea.com/65833. 
Předobjednávejte na: http://x.ea.com/65834. 

*VYŽADUJE ZÁKLADNÍ HRU THE SIMS 4 (V PRODEJI SAMOSTATNĚ) A VŠECHNY HERNÍ AKTUALIZACE. PROHLÉDNĚTE SI MINIMÁLNÍ SYSTÉMOVÉ POŽADAVKY TOHOTO BALÍČKU NA PC.
localizations.zh-TW.title: 《The Sims 4 雪國勝地》：官方遊戲預告片
localizations.zh-TW.description:
木漏隙光山的美景就在《The Sims™ 4 雪國勝地》資料片*中等著你！慢活體驗所有美好，或者快速踏上畢生難忘的冒險。更多詳情請前往：http://x.ea.com/65833。

隨著木漏隙光山的居民介紹自己的世界，獲得內行人才知道的資訊。學會欣賞此山中小鎮的文化，以及其更著名的特色，例如名聞遐邇的雪上活動以及寧靜舒適的溫泉。你已經訂好機票了嗎？

2020 年 11 月 13 日將於 PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One、和 PlayStation®4 上推出。

更多詳情請前往：http://x.ea.com/65833。
立即預購：http://x.ea.com/65834。

*需有《THE SIMS 4》主遊戲（另售）與所有遊戲更新。PC 版請參閱此資料片的最低系統需求。
localizations.zh-CN.title: 《The Sims 4 雪境仙踪》：官方游戏预告片
localizations.zh-CN.description:
树影斑驳山的奇景等您来探索，尽在《The Sims™ 4 雪境仙踪》资料片！*品味慢生活的所有美好，或一头扎进前所未有的冒险。更多信息请访问：http://x.ea.com/65833。

随着树影斑驳山的居民介绍自己的世界，获得内部人士才知道的信息。学习欣赏这个山间小镇的文化和著名特色，例如闻名遐迩的雪上活动和幽静安谧的温泉。你已经订好机票了吗？

即将于 2020 年 11 月 13 日登陆 PC/Mac、Steam、Xbox One 和 PlayStation®4。

了解更多有关此资料片的信息，请访问：http://x.ea.com/65833。
立即预购：http://x.ea.com/65834。

*需搭配《The Sims 4》（另售）并安装所有游戏更新。PC平台请参阅此资料片的最低系统要求。

snippet.title: Stardust – Official Trailer I HD I IFC Films
snippet.description:
Opening in theaters and VOD 25th

Director: Gabriel Range
Starring: Johnny Flynn, Jena Malone, Marc Maron

David Bowie is one of the most seminal legends in music history; but who was the man behind the many faces? In 1971, a 24-year-old fledgling David Bowie (Johnny Flynn) is sent to America to promote his newest record, The Man Who Sold the World. Leaving behind his pregnant wife Angie (Jena Malone), Bowie and his band embark on a makeshift coast-to-coast promotional tour with struggling Mercury Records publicist Rob Oberman (Marc Maron).

snippet.title: I Spent 24 Hours Facing My WORST Fears...
snippet.description:
I Spent 24 Hours Facing My WORST Fears...

Twitter - @grantthegoatyt

snippet.title: Ryan & Shane Get the Drunkest & Read the Most Ghost Stories • Too Many Spirits
snippet.description:
Welcome to the SEASON FINALE of our new spooky show- Too Many Spirits! Join us as we read your submitted ghost stories and enjoy cocktails prepared by first-time bartender, Steven Lim. If you've got even spookier stories, leave them in the comments below!

Please drink responsibly, and wear a mask.
This video was filmed under professional supervision. Alcohol intake was monitored, and talent was transported safely. Filming was conducted under recommended COVID-safe guidelines. 

Support us at:
http://www.patreon.com/watcher
http://www.watcherstore.com

The Wicked Watcher 
2 oz. dark rum 
3 oz. ginger beer
1 freshly squeezed lime
Lime slice garnish
2 oz. tequila (leftover from the Boozy Beergarita)

Here we have a play on a Dark n’ Stormy. But because the name of the show is Too Many Spirit, I decided to add one too many spirits, hence the two additional ounces of tequila. This one’s easy to make - poor the dark rum, ginger beer, lime juice ,tequila, and ice in a glass and stir with a bar spoon. Garnish with that good ol’ lime slice and you have yourself The Wicked Watcher. Cheers!

Created by Katie LeBlanc
Hosts - Ryan Bergara & Shane Madej
Bartender/Cam Op - Steven Lim
Stories by YOU
Editor - Stephen Castro
Production Coordinator/Sound - Brittney Lee
Head of Development - Katie LeBlanc
Creative Director of Post Production - Anthony Frederick

snippet.title: Tamar Braxton Breaks Her Silence Following Suicide Attempt
snippet.description:
Reality TV star and singer Tamar Braxton speaks publicly for the first time after her reported suicide attempt. She details her battle with depression due to her portrayal on reality TV and addresses the allegations of domestic violence with her ex-boyfriend David Adefeso.

#TamronHallShow #TamronHall #TamarBraxton

From the deeply moving to the purely fun, “Tamron Hall” is a daily destination for all things topical and a platform for viewers to connect with the people who are shaping our world through meaningful, engaging, and entertaining conversations. As a new mom, a newlywed, and a survivor who is proving you can accomplish anything at any age, Tamron Hall brings a refreshing, relatable, unpredictable, and unstoppable voice to television.
 
Broadcast from New York City featuring a dynamic mix of live and taped shows, “Tamron Hall” airs across the country in national syndication.

#MookuthiAmman Official Trailer | #RJ Balaji | #Nayanthara | NJ Saravanan | Girishh Gopalakrishnan

Presenting the Tamil trailer of Mookuthi Amman written & directed by RJ Balaji  & NJ Saravanan. The film stars Nayanthara & RJ Balaji in the lead roles. Produced by Dr.Ishari.K.Ganesh under the banner Vels Film International, Mookuthi Amman features Urvashi, Ajay Ghosh, Mouli, Smruthi Venkat in pivotal roles. snippet.title: Khabib Nurmagomedov Announces Retirement | UFC 254

snippet.title: K/DA - MORE ft. Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
Ascend the throne. K/DA is back with “MORE,” featuring Madison Beer, SOYEON and MIYEON of (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, and Seraphine.

K/DA is a virtual music supergroup by Ahri, Evelynn, Akali, and Kai’Sa. Look out for their upcoming ALL OUT EP, releasing on November 6, 2020.

Follow @KDA_MUSIC on Twitter and Instagram for updates.

LISTEN NOW:

https://ffm.to/kdamore
Spotify: https://ffm.to/kdamore-spotify
Apple Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-applemusic
YouTube Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-youtubemusic
Deezer: https://ffm.to/kdamore-deezer
Amazon Music: https://ffm.to/kdamore-amazonmusic

PRODUCTION CREDITS:

K/DA - "MORE"
Featured artists: Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine 
Written by: Riot Music Team and Bekuh BOOM
Mandarin Chinese translation by: Lexie Liu 
Korean translation by: Lydia Paek and Minji Kim
Produced by: Riot Music Team 
Executive produced by: K/DA and Seraphine 
Mixed by: Riot Music Team
Mastered by: Riot Music Team  
Vocals performed by: Madison Beer, SOYEON of (G)I-DLE, MIYEON of (G)I-DLE Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns
Additional vocals by: Bekuh BOOM
Vocal production by: Riot Music Team 
P/C Riot Games 2020

http://madisonbeer.com/
https://www.instagram.com/official_g_i_dle
https://www.instagram.com/lexieliu_
https://www.instagram.com/jairaburns
https://www.instagram.com/seradotwav
https://www.instagram.com/kda_music/

Lyrics:

K/DA
Should we show 'em how we do it everyday
(na na na)
Let's get 'em

Akali that girl
Kali go grr
Kali don’t stop
Kali don’t skrr
Kali got a job
Kali go to work
뜨거워 언제나
Don’t get burnt
넘쳐흘러 more than a buffet
난 죽여 주잖아 like I’m Buffy
누가 감히 on my huffy
거- 문 열지 마 that's a rough day

I’m giving you more
Cause I’m greater than
필요 없는 시험들
답은 이미
But all of my numbers are talking babe
부루마블 mrs 모노폴리
너는 - 종이 돈이 나는 real money
필요 없대 너네들이 많은 돈들
Go get it go get it go get it the mission
눈을 못 떼 모두 그래 너도 그래
Cause I got it different

All I’ll ever know
Is life up on a throne
시작하면 끝을 보는 거야
You want

More
Know I got it
So here you go
You look like you could use some more
Know I got it
And never running low
Yeah I got

More than enough add it up and away
You know I got it like
Bomb bomb Blow your mind
Never giving less and that’s how it’ll stay
You know I got it like
All day, All the time

When I go it’s for gold
Yeah they cool but I’m cold
I don’t fit in the mold
I’m a rebel
I don’t do what you say
Making moves I don't wait
While I smile in your face
I got different DNA

What’s higher than the top
That’s me
Come take a look
Before falling at my feet
조용히 몸을 숙여봐
So take a look
나를 기억해 a queen

Way out
感觉犹如海浪
On the wave now
不断往前遨游
Never weighed down
就是我每天想要的模样
Wow

But I know I know
You want some more
我知道你
什么要求
But I know I know
You want some more
准备好就一起走
Giving it all

Animation by Axis Studios
https://axisstudiosgroup.com/

MORE RIOT GAMES MUSIC:

https://www.youtube.com/user/RiotGamesInc/playlists?shelf_id=23&sort=dd&view=50

PLAY LEAGUE OF LEGENDS:
http://riot.com/signup

#KDA #KDAMORE #LEAGUEOFLEGENDS

snippet.title: President Donald Trump: The 60 Minutes 2020 Election Interview
snippet.description:
In an interview that's made headlines this week, Lesley Stahl presses President Trump on once-again rising coronavirus cases and what his priorities would be if re-elected. Stahl also speaks with Mr. Trump's running mate, Vice President Mike Pence. https://cbsn.ws/3mhiSZK
