Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: FINALE EPISODE | MICHELLE, NAGISA SA SARILI NIYANG MANTIKA!
snippet.description:
MAHALAGANG PAALALA:

Muli po naming pinapaalala na hanggang ngayon ay SARADO PA RIN PO ANG AMING ACTION CENTER sa TV5 Media Center, Reliance Street, Mandaluyong City.

Hindi pa rin po maaaring pumunta nang personal ang mga complainant para magreklamo kay Idol Raffy dahil sa ating kinahaharap na pandemya at mahigpit pa ring ipinapatupad ang mga safety measures upang maging ligtas ang lahat.

Gayunpaman, puwede ninyong i-PM ang inyong mga sumbong sa OFFICIAL Facebook page ni Idol na RAFFY TULFO IN ACTION na may mahigit 11M followers. Nakahanda pong tumugon sa inyo ang RTIA researchers.

Maraming salamat sa inyong pag-unawa at mag-ingat po tayong lahat!

snippet.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《倖存者 Drifter》Official Music Video
snippet.description:
JJ 林俊傑 第14張專輯《倖存者 • 如你》雙EP 
雙維度 EP 創造全新音樂視角 

數位收聽｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJDrifterLikeYouDoYC
實體購買｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJXIVFA

林俊傑 x 賴雅妍 x 修杰楷
張榮吉 執導x 余靜萍 掌鏡 
高規格團隊打造 城市中最暖的視覺感官

城市中承載著多少偉大的夢想、渺小的希望
世界上又有多少角落的失望、低頭的沮喪
倖存於世界、倖存於社會
但，是否倖存於自己的內心所愛？

人來人往忙碌的現代世界，“冷漠“成為了生活進步的產物，JJ跳脫以往掏空內心的訴說方式，套入每個人的故事去唱「你我他的故事」。同為如此忙碌的現代人，長遠的夢想、或眼前的目標，就像傳輸帶一般被推著走的生活，努力追求似乎是唯一的解答，試圖拋出“快樂的定義是什麼？“，希望在每個可能重整的狀態中，能夠啟發不斷重新定義人生跟社會。

JJ 以口述的語氣，就像是一個低語的自我訴說者，化為每一位低頭專注自己世界的過客，知名作詞人小寒，用堅毅且剛硬的語句映出每個人為了過想過的生活，就像是一場戰爭，但字裡行間透露著內心深處的脆弱與無力，每一個肯定句，都在為自己的生命打氣，而最終在曲末扣回生命主體“愛”，將歌曲的溫度在經歷曲勢的猛烈炙燒後，停留在一個剛好適合取暖的溫度。

MV由 張榮吉執導、余靜萍掌鏡，兩人對畫面的默契以及對故事的詮釋，故事看似不相干的兩個時空，但藉由男主角對生命的熱情與對環境的傾力，讓兩個時空串起了密不可分的關係，而JJ依然以客串的姿態出現在自己的MV裡面，並接續著【交換餘生】的概念，扮演著兩個時空的連接點。

#JJ林俊傑倖存者
#JJ林俊傑倖存者如你
#JJDrifter
#JJDrifterLikeYouDo
#JJXIV #JJDoubleEP

_
倖存者    詞：小寒  曲：林俊傑

冷掉的飯盒 台詞對半摺
渴 這時候算什麼
而 心涼如薄荷 脆弱如蛋殼 
則 消失在這一刻

背著夢的倖存者 經過現實的拉扯
可 贏得了拔河 理念還剩幾毫克 
背負傷的倖存者 爭奪著有限名額
可 留下的有幾個  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
等著有了起色  
我要傷悄悄地癒合 命運別招惹 
  
曾想出爾 反爾 奈何
我宣言還言猶在耳
得對自己比別人對我嚴格  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
忍著有了起色   
我是否賺取了資格 可以來到這
生還不為巧合 或聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可

背著夢的倖存者 經歷生活的牽扯
可 持續的拔河 眼神可還會灼熱
背負傷的倖存者 代價是感情全額
可 我如何做取捨 嗚

夢的光澤在溫和應和   
是燈蛾總認得月兒
人生來就會漂流向 發著光的誘餌
  
雖然偶爾 我偶爾 想為何 
但諾言還言猶在耳
想要閃爍就對自己更嚴格 

夢的光澤在溫和地應和   
燈蛾不由得分隔
我是否已賺取了資格 可以站在這
生還不為巧合 或能聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可
真的
_

snippet.localized.title: 林俊傑 JJ Lin《倖存者 Drifter》Official Music Video
snippet.localized.description:
JJ 林俊傑 第14張專輯《倖存者 • 如你》雙EP 
雙維度 EP 創造全新音樂視角 

數位收聽｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJDrifterLikeYouDoYC
實體購買｜https://jjlin.lnk.to/JJXIVFA

林俊傑 x 賴雅妍 x 修杰楷
張榮吉 執導x 余靜萍 掌鏡 
高規格團隊打造 城市中最暖的視覺感官

城市中承載著多少偉大的夢想、渺小的希望
世界上又有多少角落的失望、低頭的沮喪
倖存於世界、倖存於社會
但，是否倖存於自己的內心所愛？

人來人往忙碌的現代世界，“冷漠“成為了生活進步的產物，JJ跳脫以往掏空內心的訴說方式，套入每個人的故事去唱「你我他的故事」。同為如此忙碌的現代人，長遠的夢想、或眼前的目標，就像傳輸帶一般被推著走的生活，努力追求似乎是唯一的解答，試圖拋出“快樂的定義是什麼？“，希望在每個可能重整的狀態中，能夠啟發不斷重新定義人生跟社會。

JJ 以口述的語氣，就像是一個低語的自我訴說者，化為每一位低頭專注自己世界的過客，知名作詞人小寒，用堅毅且剛硬的語句映出每個人為了過想過的生活，就像是一場戰爭，但字裡行間透露著內心深處的脆弱與無力，每一個肯定句，都在為自己的生命打氣，而最終在曲末扣回生命主體“愛”，將歌曲的溫度在經歷曲勢的猛烈炙燒後，停留在一個剛好適合取暖的溫度。

MV由 張榮吉執導、余靜萍掌鏡，兩人對畫面的默契以及對故事的詮釋，故事看似不相干的兩個時空，但藉由男主角對生命的熱情與對環境的傾力，讓兩個時空串起了密不可分的關係，而JJ依然以客串的姿態出現在自己的MV裡面，並接續著【交換餘生】的概念，扮演著兩個時空的連接點。

#JJ林俊傑倖存者
#JJ林俊傑倖存者如你
#JJDrifter
#JJDrifterLikeYouDo
#JJXIV #JJDoubleEP

_
倖存者    詞：小寒  曲：林俊傑

冷掉的飯盒 台詞對半摺
渴 這時候算什麼
而 心涼如薄荷 脆弱如蛋殼 
則 消失在這一刻

背著夢的倖存者 經過現實的拉扯
可 贏得了拔河 理念還剩幾毫克 
背負傷的倖存者 爭奪著有限名額
可 留下的有幾個  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
等著有了起色  
我要傷悄悄地癒合 命運別招惹 
  
曾想出爾 反爾 奈何
我宣言還言猶在耳
得對自己比別人對我嚴格  

有苦澀 忐忑 坎坷 
忍著有了起色   
我是否賺取了資格 可以來到這
生還不為巧合 或聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可

背著夢的倖存者 經歷生活的牽扯
可 持續的拔河 眼神可還會灼熱
背負傷的倖存者 代價是感情全額
可 我如何做取捨 嗚

夢的光澤在溫和應和   
是燈蛾總認得月兒
人生來就會漂流向 發著光的誘餌
  
雖然偶爾 我偶爾 想為何 
但諾言還言猶在耳
想要閃爍就對自己更嚴格 

夢的光澤在溫和地應和   
燈蛾不由得分隔
我是否已賺取了資格 可以站在這
生還不為巧合 或能聞名遐邇
只是為了得到愛的人 認可
真的
_

localizations.ja.description: 4年間以上の同僚生活とトレーニングがあるから、BLACKPINKのメンバーがお互いの性格と習慣について話す。リサのフレンドリー性格とロゼの適応性はタイムトラベラーに1番相応しいこと。そしてジスとジェニーは海外ショッピングについてどうやってお得なお買い上げを出来る情報もシェアします。

localizations.zh-Hans.description: 經過四年來一起訓練以及一起住宿舍的時間，BLACKPINK證明了她們對彼此的生活習慣有著徹底的了解。Lisa的友善以及Rosé的適應能力讓她們成為最有潛力的時光旅行者。Jisoo以及Jennie也分享了一些个人秘诀，能帮助他们在海外购物时获得最优惠的价格。

localizations.id.title: BLACKPINK memberitahu anggapan mereka tentang satu sama lain | Siapa, Aku? [INDO SUB]
localizations.id.description: Setelah latihan dan hidup bersama lebih dari 4 tahun, BLACKPINK menunjukkan pengetahuan tingkat atas mereka tentang sifat dan kebiasaan satu sama lain. Kami jadi tahu kalau keramahan Lisa dan kemampuan beradaptasi Rosé membuat mereka calon penjelajah waktu terbaik, lalu Jisoo dan Jennie berbagi tips pribadi tentang cara dapat harga murah saat belanja di luar negeri.
localizations.th.title: BLACKPINK บอกเราว่าพวกเธอคิดต่อกันอย่างไรกันแน่ | ใครกัน ฉันเหรอ? [ซับไทย]
localizations.th.description: ด้วยประสบการณ์การฝึกและอยู่ด้วยกันมานานกว่าสี่ปี BLACKPINK โชว์ความรู้ขั้นกว่าของนิสัยของสมาชิก ความเป็นมิตรของลิซ่าและการปรับตัวเก่งของโรเซ่ทำให้พวกเธอน่าจะเป็นนักท่องเวลาที่ดีที่สุด จีซูและเจนนี่ให้เคล็ดลับส่วนตัวยามที่ไปช้อปปิ้งต่างประเทศ

snippet.title: Ask TSL: Questions Girls Always Wanted To Ask Guys
snippet.description:
In this episode of Ask TSL, we got our MANLIEST MEN to answer questions we got from our females viewers. Let me just tell you, it got HECTIC!

Here are the questions that were answered:
0:00 - Introduction
0:40 - Do men feel intimidated when their girlfriends/ wives earn more than them?
1:43 - If a couple begins to live together, how should duties like household chores and child rearing be split?
2:48 - Are girls who are short and small more attractive?
4:05 - Where do guys go for relationship advice?
6:05 - Are attention-seeking girls irritating, or do guys actually find that cute?
7:03 - Do guys share about their sex lives with their bros?
8:15 - Why is marriage so terrifying for many guys?
9:58 - Why do some men have mostly female friends? Is that a red flag?
11:08 - Does a female’s attractiveness drop if she wishes to get intimate on the first date?
12:43 - Occasionally, some girls can get bitchy about how other girls look, is it the same for guys?
13:46 - What do you think about periods?
15:43 - What are some things that females have misconceptions of?
16:53 - Guys in Singapore are quite passive and shy when it comes to dating, but are intimidated when a girl asks them out. What’s going on?!
18:05 - What are your thoughts when girls say that ‘men are trash’?
20:26 - Outro & Thoughts

snippet.title: SEVENTEEN (세븐틴) 'HOME;RUN' Official MV
snippet.description:
SEVENTEEN (세븐틴) 'HOME;RUN' Official MV

세븐틴의 이번 앨범 ‘; [Semicolon]’은 미니 7집 ‘헹가래’를 통해 이야기한 ‘청춘’을 향한 응원의 메시지를 다시금 공유하면서 한 발짝 더 나아가 쉼 없이 달리는 청춘에게 ‘잠깐 쉬어가며 청춘의 향연을 즐기자’라는 더욱 성숙한 긍정의 메시지를 전하는 앨범이다.

현 시대를 살아가며 고군분투 하고 있는 청춘들에게 잠시나마 ‘숨 고를 시간’, ‘함께 웃으며 즐길 수 있는 시간’을 문장을 잠시 끊었다가 이어서 설명을 계속할 때 쓰이는 문장 부호인 ‘Semicolon(세미콜론)’ 에 비유, 동시대 청춘으로 살아가는 “세븐틴” 그들의 공감을 전하는 메시지를 앨범에 가득 담아내어 청춘들을 어루만질 따뜻한 위로와 응원, 공감을 주는 희망의 외침을 전한다.

타이틀곡 ‘HOME;RUN’은 스윙 장르 기반의 레트로한 사운드가 돋보이는 곡으로 경쾌하고 타격감 넘치는 사운드로 ‘HOME RUN’이라는 표현이 지닌 짜릿함을 표현하였고, 무한한 성장을 지닌 청춘에게 힘찬 응원과 위로의 목소리를 선사한다.

SEVENTEEN’s new album ‘; [Semicolon]’ is an album where they share the encouraging message for the ‘youth’ like they did in their 7th mini album ‘Heng:garæ’ and also the positive message that ‘we should all take a break and enjoy the youth’ with the youth that are running towards their goals without any breaks.

‘Semicolon,’ which is a punctuation mark used when you pause a sentence and then resume again, is used as a metaphor to portray the ‘time to take a breath’ and ‘time to laugh and enjoy together.’ “SEVENTEEN,” as the youth who are living in the same time period as the other youth who are fighting alone and struggling through their lives, uses this metaphor to convey their hopeful and empathic message through the album to comfort and cheer for the youth.

The title song ‘HOME;RUN’ is a song based on swing genre where the retro-like sound stands out, and it portrays the excitement that the phrase ‘HOME RUN’ conveys with cheerful and rhythmical sound. It conveys powerful support and comfort to the youth with limitless potentials.

#SEVENTEEN #세븐틴
#Semicolon #세미콜론
#HOME_RUN

localizations.ko.title: SEVENTEEN (세븐틴) 'HOME;RUN' Official MV
localizations.ko.description:
SEVENTEEN (세븐틴) 'HOME;RUN' Official MV

세븐틴의 이번 앨범 ‘; [Semicolon]’은 미니 7집 ‘헹가래’를 통해 이야기한 ‘청춘’을 향한 응원의 메시지를 다시금 공유하면서 한 발짝 더 나아가 쉼 없이 달리는 청춘에게 ‘잠깐 쉬어가며 청춘의 향연을 즐기자’라는 더욱 성숙한 긍정의 메시지를 전하는 앨범이다.

현 시대를 살아가며 고군분투 하고 있는 청춘들에게 잠시나마 ‘숨 고를 시간’, ‘함께 웃으며 즐길 수 있는 시간’을 문장을 잠시 끊었다가 이어서 설명을 계속할 때 쓰이는 문장 부호인 ‘Semicolon(세미콜론)’ 에 비유, 동시대 청춘으로 살아가는 “세븐틴” 그들의 공감을 전하는 메시지를 앨범에 가득 담아내어 청춘들을 어루만질 따뜻한 위로와 응원, 공감을 주는 희망의 외침을 전한다.

타이틀곡 ‘HOME;RUN’은 스윙 장르 기반의 레트로한 사운드가 돋보이는 곡으로 경쾌하고 타격감 넘치는 사운드로 ‘HOME RUN’이라는 표현이 지닌 짜릿함을 표현하였고, 무한한 성장을 지닌 청춘에게 힘찬 응원과 위로의 목소리를 선사한다.

SEVENTEEN’s new album ‘; [Semicolon]’ is an album where they share the encouraging message for the ‘youth’ like they did in their 7th mini album ‘Heng:garæ’ and also the positive message that ‘we should all take a break and enjoy the youth’ with the youth that are running towards their goals without any breaks.

‘Semicolon,’ which is a punctuation mark used when you pause a sentence and then resume again, is used as a metaphor to portray the ‘time to take a breath’ and ‘time to laugh and enjoy together.’ “SEVENTEEN,” as the youth who are living in the same time period as the other youth who are fighting alone and struggling through their lives, uses this metaphor to convey their hopeful and empathic message through the album to comfort and cheer for the youth.

The title song ‘HOME;RUN’ is a song based on swing genre where the retro-like sound stands out, and it portrays the excitement that the phrase ‘HOME RUN’ conveys with cheerful and rhythmical sound. It conveys powerful support and comfort to the youth with limitless potentials.

#SEVENTEEN #세븐틴
#Semicolon #세미콜론
#HOME_RUN

snippet.title: President Donald Trump: The 60 Minutes 2020 Election Interview
snippet.description:
In an interview that's made headlines this week, Lesley Stahl presses President Trump on once-again rising coronavirus cases and what his priorities would be if re-elected. Stahl also speaks with Mr. Trump's running mate, Vice President Mike Pence. https://cbsn.ws/3mhiSZK

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu
Watch Full Episodes of 60 Minutes HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Qkjo1F
Get more 60 Minutes from 60 Minutes: Overtime HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1KG3sdr
Relive past episodes and interviews with 60 Minutes Rewind HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1PlZiGI
Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

snippet.title: Joe Biden: The 60 Minutes 2020 Election Interview
snippet.description:
The former vice president talks with Norah O'Donnell about the pandemic, taxes, the Supreme Court, and the "stark" differences between himself and President Trump. O'Donnell also speaks with Mr. Biden's running mate, California Senator Kamala Harris. https://cbsn.ws/3mhiSZK

Subscribe to the 60 Minutes Channel HERE: http://bit.ly/1S7CLRu
Watch Full Episodes of 60 Minutes HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Qkjo1F
Get more 60 Minutes from 60 Minutes: Overtime HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1KG3sdr
Relive past episodes and interviews with 60 Minutes Rewind HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1PlZiGI
Follow 60 Minutes on Instagram HERE: http://bit.ly/23Xv8Ry
Like 60 Minutes on Facebook HERE: http://on.fb.me/1Xb1Dao
Follow 60 Minutes on Twitter HERE: http://bit.ly/1KxUsqX

Get the latest news and best in original reporting from CBS News delivered to your inbox. Subscribe to newsletters HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1RqHw7T

Get your news on the go! Download CBS News mobile apps HERE: http://cbsn.ws/1Xb1WC8

Get new episodes of shows you love across devices the next day, stream local news live, and watch full seasons of CBS fan favorites anytime, anywhere with CBS All Access. Try it free! http://bit.ly/1OQA29B

---
60 Minutes, the most successful American television broadcast in history, began its 52nd season in September. Offering hard-hitting investigative reports, interviews, feature segments and profiles of people in the news, the broadcast began in 1968 is still a hit in 2020. 60 Minutes makes Nielsen’s weekly Top 10 nearly every week and was the #1 weekly television broadcast three times last season.


The program still averages more than 10 million viewers, more than double the audience of its nearest network news magazine competitor. The average audience for a 60 Minutes broadcast is 150% higher than those of the network morning news programs; the audience dwarfs the number of viewers drawn by the most popular cable news programs.  


About a million more people listen to the 60 Minutes radio simulcast in several major cities and on its companion podcast. Tens of thousands each week experience 60 Minutes online. The broadcast’s segments can be watched at 60Minutes.com and on the CBS All Access app. Its webcast, 60MinutesOvertime.com, offers content originally produced for the web, including behind-the-scenes video about the production of 60 Minutes stories and timely archival segments.


60 Minutes has won every major broadcast award. Its 25 Peabody and 150 Emmy awards are the most won by any single news program. It has also won 20 duPont-Columbia University journalism awards. Other distinguished journalism honors won multiple times include the George Polk, RTDNA Edward R. Murrow, Investigative Reporters and Editors, RFK Journalism, Sigma Delta Chi and Gerald Loeb awards.

60 Minutes premiered on CBS September 24, 1968. Bill Owens is the program’s executive producer. The correspondents and contributors of 60 Minutes are Sharyn Alfonsi, Anderson Cooper, John Dickerson, Norah O’Donnell, Scott Pelley, Lesley Stahl, Bill Whitaker and L. Jon Wertheim.

Besteige den Thron. K/DA kehrt mit dem Lied „MORE“, gesungen von Madison Beer, SOYEON und MIYEON von (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns und Seraphine, zurück.

K/DA ist eine virtuelle Musikgruppe, die aus Ahri, Evelynn, Akali und Kai’Sa besteht. Halte nach der neuen Platte „ALL OUT“ Ausschau, die am 6. November 2020 veröffentlicht wird.

Folge @KDA_MUSIC auf Twitter und Instagram für Neuigkeiten.

localizations.hu.title: K/DA–MORE, előadja: Madison Beer, (G)I-DLE, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, Seraphine(hivatalos zenei videó)
localizations.hu.description:
Irány a trón. A K/DA visszatért a „MORE” című dalával, amely Madison Beer, a (G)I-DLE tagjai, SOYEON és MIYEON, Lexie Liu, Jaira Burns, valamint Seraphine közreműködésével készült.

A K/DA egy virtuális zenei szupercsapat, amelynek tagja Ahri, Evelynn, Akali és Kai’Sa. Tartsd nyitva a szemed, az ALL OUT című album 2020. november 6-án érkezik.

A friss hírekért kövesd a @KDA_MUSIC-ot a Twitteren és az Instagramon.

Episode 153: A Laughter Riot With Riteish And Genelia
------------------------------------------------------
Riteish and Genelia are the guests in today's episode. The husband and wife share their funny memories about their marriage life. Krishna and Kiku make a funny appearance in between to entertain. Watch the full episode to know more.

About The Kapil Sharma Show Season 2 : 
----------------------------------------------------------------
Kapil Sharma is back with a new 'Salah Center' (Consultancy Business) in a Mohollah with absurd characters. The wealthy milkman Bachcha Yadav (Kiku Sharda) with his wife Titli Yadav (Bharti Singh) and sister-in-law Bhoori (Sumona Singh) is the one who has rented out houses within the Mohollah and is Kapil Sharma's business partner. The neighbors in the Mohollah are also full of quirks and don't shy away from the antics. With celebrities gracing every episode, The Kapil Sharma Show promises fun-filled entertaining weekends.

snippet.title: Geoengineering: A Horrible Idea We Might Have to Do
snippet.description:
To support Kurzgesagt and learn more about Brilliant, go to https://www.brilliant.org/nutshell and sign up for free. The first 200 people that go to that link will get 20% off the annual Premium subscription.
Thanks to our friends from Brilliant for supporting this channel.

Sources & further reading: 
https://sites.google.com/view/sourcesgeoengineering
 
By the end of the 21st century, humanity is becoming desperate. Decades of heatwaves and droughts have led to unusually  poor harvests, while the warming oceans yield fewer fish each year. In the tropical zones, millions suffer from famine and resource wars have made millions more flee to the north. As things quickly get worse, in an act of desperation, the world's governments decide to enact an emergency plan...
It is far from certain that a grim scenario like this will play out. But the failure of world leaders  to effectively address climate change, makes it far from impossible. 
So in the near future it might become necessary to try something radical to slow down rapid climate change: Geoengineering. Interventions so massive in scale that they might undo centuries of human behavior. Or make everything much worse.
What is geoengineering, is it really an option and what if it goes wrong?

snippet.title: Among Us But Its A Reality Show 3
snippet.description:
🎬BEHIND THE SCENES: https://youtu.be/ozufblAjQQw
GET THE MERCH: https://teespring.com/stores/among-us-lol

There are two imposters among us again. After lots of band-aids and medbay visits, our friends are back and better than ever, and as usual are hurling through the dark and unforgiving spacescape with nothing but their tiny brains and a maddening amount of terrible arguments. Our group has to figure out who on the ship are murderers, while making sure they are doing their tasks so that their spaceship doesn't continue its forward frontflipping momentum. Is red sus or is blue? Who should we vote out? Which player is the imposter venting to kill? Will people be murdered by the imposter or by their beloved crewmates? Find out in this week's third episode of Among Us but it's a reality show.

snippet.title: Trump Now Crashing In 2020 As Some Fans Bolt, Echoing Trump U. Debacle | MSNBC
snippet.description:
New 2020 polls from six key states show some Trump 2016 voters abandoning him -- imperiling his narrow coalition. MSNBC's Ari Melber reports on why both the loyalty and enmity among Trump fans is different than for other politicians; and Melber documents how Trump customers turned on his con in the "Trump University" case and explores the parallels to Trump's political standing today. (This interview is from MSNBC’s “The Beat with Ari Melber, a news show covering politics, law and culture airing nightly at 6pm ET on MSNBC. http://www.thebeatwithari.com). Aired on 10/19/2020.
» Subscribe to MSNBC: http://on.msnbc.com/SubscribeTomsnbc

About The Beat with Ari Melber: Former lawyer Ari Melber leads this show that provides in-depth analysis of the day's biggest news stories. ""The Beat"" features guest interviews in addition to reporting on stories from across the country. The stories that are covered span across the political spectrum. In addition to his law background, Melber is a former Senate staffer, giving him a unique perspective to share on the political happenings coming out of Washington, D.C.

MSNBC delivers breaking news, in-depth analysis of politics headlines, as well as commentary and informed perspectives. 시작하면 끝을 보는 거야
You want

More
Know I got it
So here you go
You look like you could use some more
Know I got it
And never running low
Yeah I got

More than enough add it up and away
You know I got it like
Bomb bomb Blow your mind

You know I got it like
All day, All the time

When I go it’s for gold

I’m a rebel
I don’t do what you say
Making moves I don't wait
While I smile in your face
I got different DNA

What’s higher than the top
That’s me
Come take a look
Before falling at my feet
조용히 몸을 숙여봐
So take a look
나를 기억해 a queen

Way out
感觉犹如海浪
On the wave now
不断往前遨游
Never weighed down
就是我每天想要的模样
Wow

But I know I know
You want some more
我知道你
什么要求
But I know I know
You want some more
准备好就一起走
Giving it all

snippet.title: POR QUE A BOLSA NÃO PARA DE CAIR? | O IBOVESPA CAIU 4,25%
snippet.description:
Entre na lista de espera da mentoria Do Mil ao Milhão: https://bit.ly/3krRlUH

Inscreva-se no nosso NOVO CANAL PRIMOCAST: https://bit.ly/3hJOapA

3 principais acontecimentos:

1 - Segunda onda de coronavirus: França e agora provavelmente Alemanha irão mais uma vez ter lockdown por 1 mês. Isso significa, em outras palavras, que a economia deles pode ficar parada mais 1 mês. Além disso, a Inglaterra também está dando sinais de pressão pra fazer um novo lockdown.

Isso por si só não seria muito problema, mas a aversão a risco do mercado apitou o alerta, já que a vitória do Biden nos Estados Unidos parece provável, E, com ele na presidência, existe a possibilidade do mercado americano fazer a mesma coisa.

Por conta disso, o mercado reagiu muito mal, e isso refletiu também na nossa bolsa.

2 - Hoje é dia de COPOM, e, uma coisa pode-se dizer que tem refletido muito mal na nossa economia: o descasamento cada vez mais preocupante entre taxa de juros e inflação. Enquanto a taxa de juros provavelmente continuará em 2% (tudo no mercado sinaliza isso), a inflação está subindo, já que o IPCA está em 3,14% nos últimos 12 meses (acima da taxa Selic)

3 - A Petrobras aprovou a revisão da política de remuneração aos acionistas, de forma que a companhia possa pagar dividendo mesmo sem ter registrado lucro. As ações da Petr4 caíram, e como ela sozinha representa cerca de 8% do Ibovespa (e outras ações que compõem também caíram bastante), isso contribuiu para que o Ibovespa tivesse a queda que está tendo hoje.

INFORMACJE O GRZE
Wskakujcie do Wild Rift: testującej umiejętności i strategie gry MOBA 5 na 5 stworzonej od podstaw na bazie League of Legends specjalnie z myślą o urządzeniach przenośnych (i wkrótce, konsolach). Korzystając z nowego sterowania i szybkiego tempa meczów, gracze o dowolnym poziomie umiejętności mogą połączyć siły ze znajomymi, wybrać swojego bohatera i pokazać, na co ich stać. 

Więcej na https://wildrift.leagueoflegends.com/pl-pl/.

snippet.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise to new heights in Apex Legends Season 7 on the floating city of Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

There’s a whole new world waiting to be explored. The stakes are higher and the falls are deadlier on Olympus. New Legend Horizon understands the gravity of the situation, and she’s sure to give the other Legends a lift -- whether they want it or not. Plus hop on Olympus’s floating Trident vehicles, grab the latest Battle Pass, ascend to the top of Ranked, and build your community with Clubs. Up your game when Season 7 releases on November 4.

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. And play on Steam when Season 7 launches on November 4 !  

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

#MeetHorizon #ApexSeason7 #ApexSeason7 #ApexLegends

“Ain’t Our Time To Die (Champions of Justice Remix)”
Performed by DOROTHY

localizations.de-DE.title: Apex Legends Saison 7 – Aufstieg-Launch-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Starte deinen Höhenflug in Apex Legends Saison 7 auf der schwebenden Stadt Olympus  http://x.ea.com/65921

Erkunde eine völlig neue Welt. Auf Olympus ist der Einsatz höher und jeder Sturz noch tödlicher. Die neue Legende, Horizon, weiß um den Ernst der Lage und hilft den anderen Legenden auf die Sprünge – ob sie wollen oder nicht. Drehe auf Olympus außerdem eine Runde mit den schwebenden Tridents, hol dir den neuesten Battle Pass, klettere an die Spitze der Rangliste und baue mit Clubs deine eigene Community auf. Bringe dein Spiel voran, wenn Saison 7 am 5. November erscheint.

Apex Legends™ ist ein Free-to-Play-Battle-Royale-Spiel, bei dem legendäre Charaktere am Rande des Grenzlands um Ruhm und Reichtum kämpfen. Jetzt kostenlos auf Xbox One, PS4 sowie Steam und Origin für PC spielen.

localizations.pt-PT.title: Apex Legends Temporada 7 – Trailer de Lançamento de Ascension
localizations.pt-PT.description:
Sobe a novas alturas na cidade flutuante de Olympus com a Temporada 7 de Apex Legends  http://x.ea.com/65921

Há um mundo à espera de ser explorado. Em Olympus, o risco é grande e as quedas são ainda maiores. Horizon, a nova Lenda, compreende a gravidade da situação e está pronta para dar um empurrãozinho aos seus adversários, quer eles queiram quer não... Podes ainda sentar-te ao volante dos veículos flutuantes Trident, agarrar o mais recente Battle Pass, atingir o topo da classificação e contribuir para a comunidade com os Clubs. Melhora o teu jogo a 4 de novembro com o arranque da Temporada 7.

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito do género battle royale onde personagens lendárias lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nas periferias da Fronteira. Joga já de graça na Xbox One, PS4, Steam e Origin para PC.

localizations.fr-FR.title: Trailer de lancement de la saison 7 d’Apex Legends - Ascension
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Atteignez de nouveaux sommets pendant la saison 7 d'Apex Legends en explorant la ville flottante d'Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Explorez un tout nouveau monde. À Olympus, les enjeux sont de taille et les chutes mortelles. La nouvelle Légende Horizon est consciente de la gravité de la situation et compte se faire entendre auprès des autres Légendes, que ce soit de gré ou de force. Découvrez le Trident, un aéroglisseur qui vous aidera à traverser Olympus à toute vitesse, obtenez le nouveau Passe de combat, progressez dans les ligues classées et développez votre communauté grâce au système de clubs. Préparez-vous pour la saison 7, qui débutera le 4 novembre.

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation 4, Xbox One et Steam ou Origin pour PC.

localizations.no.title: Apex Legends – Sesong 7 – Ascension-lanseringstrailer
localizations.no.description:
Nå nye høyder i den 7. sesongen av Apex Legends, som finner sted i den svevende byen Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden venter på å bli utforsket. Enda mer står på spill og høydene blir enda farligere på Olympus. Den nye legenden Horizon forstår byrden situasjonen byr på, og hun kan gi de andre legendene et løft – enten de vil det eller ei. Hopp ombord i de svevende Trident-kjøretøyene på Olympus, skaff deg spillets nye Battle Pass, nå toppen i rangerte kamper og etabler ditt eget fellesskap med klubber. Ta spillet til nye høyder når sesong 7 lanseres 4. november.

Apex Legends™ er et gratis battle royale-spill hvor legendariske karakterer kjemper om rikdom og ære i utkanten av grenselandet. Spill gratis på Xbox One, PS4 og Steam og Origin for PC nå.

localizations.it.title: Apex Legends - Stagione 7 - Ascensione - Il trailer di lancio
localizations.it.description:
Raggiungi nuove vette ed esplora la città sospesa di Olympus nella Stagione 7 di Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un mondo inesplorato ti aspetta. A Olympus, il pericolo è sempre in agguato e gli errori non lasciano scampo. La nuova leggenda Horizon conosce la... gravità della situazione ed è pronta a tirare su le altre leggende, che lo vogliano o meno. Usa i Trident per spostarti in giro per la mappa, ottieni il nuovo pass battaglia, scala le vette della competizione nella modalità Classificata e crea la tua community con i club. Dai il massimo nella Stagione 7, in arrivo il 4 novembre.

Apex Legends™ è un gioco gratuito in stile battle royale in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su Xbox One, PlayStation 4, e Steam e Origin per PC.

localizations.pl.title: Zwiastun sezonu 7. Apex Legends: Wstąpienie
localizations.pl.description:
Wznies się na wyżyny w 7. sezonie Apex Legends w latającym mieście Olimp.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Nowy świat czeka na odkrycie. Na Olimpie stawki są większe, a upadki bardziej bolesne. Nowa legenda, Horizon, dobrze zdaje sobie sprawę z wagi sytuacji i chętnie pomoże pozostałym legendom – czy tego chcą, czy nie. Wsiądźcie do latających pojazdów Olimpu, Trójzębów, i sprawcie sobie nową przepustkę bojową, pnijcie się na szczyt rankingu i rozwijajcie społeczność w Klubach. Pozwól rozgrywce wstąpić na wyższy poziom z premierą 7. sezonu już 4 listopada.

Apex Legends™ to darmowa gra Battle Royale, w której legendarne postacie mierzą się ze sobą w walce o sławę i chwałę na obrzeżach Kresów. Graj w Apex Legends za darmo już teraz – na Xbox One, PlayStation 4, Steam oraz Origin na PC.

localizations.ja.title: 「エーペックスレジェンズ シーズン7 – アセンション」ローンチトレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
空中都市オリンパスへ向かい、「エーペックスレジェンズ」シーズン7で新たな高みを目指せ。http://x.ea.com/65921

まったく新しい未知の世界が広がる。オリンパスはこれまで以上の危険をはらみ、落下の影響はこれまでの比ではない。新レジェンドのホライゾンはその重大性を認識し、重力を熟知する存在。他のレジェンドが望むと望まざるに関わらず、空中へと巻き上げてしまう。オリンパスでは飛行型ビークル「トライデント」に乗り込み、バトルパスを手にしてランクシリーズの上位を目指そう。新登場の「クラブ」機能を使って自身のコミュニティを作ることも可能だ。11月4日、シーズン7で高みを目指せ。

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One、PS4、Steam、Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

localizations.es-ES.title: Temporada 7 de Apex Legends: tráiler de lanzamiento de Ascenso
localizations.es-ES.description:
Alcanza nuevas cotas en la temporada 7 de Apex Legends en la ciudad flotante de Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Explora un mundo completamente nuevo. En Olympus, hay muchísimo en juego y las caídas son más letales. Horizon, la nueva leyenda, entiende la gravedad de la situación y acabará lanzando a otras leyendas por los aires (quieran o no). Además, súbete a los vehículos flotantes Trident de Olympus, hazte con el último pase de batalla, alcanza la cima de la clasificación y forma una comunidad con los clubes. Mejora tu juego con el lanzamiento de la temporada 7 el 4 de noviembre.

Apex Legends™ es un juego de Battle Royale gratuito donde personajes legendarios se enfrentan para lograr gloria, fama y fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega ya gratis en Xbox One, PS4 y Steam y Origin para PC.

localizations.zh-Hans.title: 《Apex Legends》第 7 赛季 – 冲上云霄发布预告片
localizations.zh-Hans.description:
参加《Apex Legends》第 7 赛季，光临漂浮城市“奥林匹斯”，达到全新高度。http://x.ea.com/65921

有一个全新的世界等着我们去探索。奥林匹斯这里赌注更大，而致命程度也更高。全新传奇地平线，她了解引力，而且能让其他传奇悬浮──无论他们愿不愿意。跳上奥林匹斯的“三叉戟”漂浮载具，入手最新的战斗通行证，登上排位赛之巅，并以“俱乐部”来组建你的社区。就在 11 月 4 日第 7 赛季推出时大显身手。

《Apex Legends™》是一款免费大逃杀游戏，传奇角色们在边境边缘为荣誉、名望和财富而战。赶快在 Xbox One、PS4 和 PC 端 Steam 与 Origin 上免费游玩。

localizations.zh-Hant.title: 《Apex 英雄》賽季 7 - 飛升發行預告片
localizations.zh-Hant.description:
在《Apex 英雄》賽季 7 的漂浮城市「奧林匹斯」中達到新高度。 http://x.ea.com/65921

一個全新的世界等你來探索。在奧林匹斯這裡賭注更大，而致命程度也更高。新英雄天際線，她了解引力，而且能讓其他英雄懸浮──無論他們願不願意。另外，登上奧林匹斯的懸浮「三叉戟」載具、取得最新的戰鬥通行證、提升積分排名，並使用「俱樂部」打造你的社群。就在 11 月 4 日賽季 7 推出時大顯身手。

《Apex 英雄》是一款可免費遊玩的大逃殺遊戲，傳說中的角色們將在邊境的遠處，為榮耀、名聲與財富而戰。立即在 Xbox One、PS4、PC Origin 與 Steam 上免費遊玩。

localizations.ko.description:
Apex 레전드 시즌 7에서 새로운 천공의 도시 올림푸스로 떠오르십시오.  http://x.ea.com/65921

완전히 새로운 세계를 탐험하십시오. 높은 고도의 올림푸스에서는 위험도 더 커집니다. 신규 레전드 호라이즌은 중력만큼이나 중대한 상황을 이해하며, 다른 레전드를 높이 띄워 줍니다. 원하지 않더라도 말이죠. 올림푸스의 부양 트라이던트 차량에 타보고, 최신 배틀 패스를 손에 넣고 랭크의 최상위로 뛰어오르며 클럽을 만들어 공동체를 운영하십시오. 11월 4일 시즌7으로 게임의 수준을 한층 더 높이십시오.

Apex 레전드™는 전설적인 캐릭터들이 영광과 명성, 부를 쟁취하기 위해 프런티어의 변경에서 치열한 전투를 벌이는 부분 유료 배틀 로얄 게임입니다. Xbox One, PlayStation 4 및 PC용 Steam 및 Origin에서 Apex 레전드를 무료 플레이하십시오.

localizations.ar.description:
ارتق إلى مستويات جديدة في الموسم 7 من Apex Legends في مدينة Olympus الطافية.  http://x.ea.com/65921

هنالك عالم جديد بالكامل في انتظارك لكي تستكشفه. إن المخاطر عالية والإخفاقات أشد فتكًا في Olympus. الأسطورة الجديدة Horizon تعي خطورة الموقف, وسوف تحرص على تقديم المساعدة للجميع, سواء أرادوا ذلك أم لا. بالإضافة إلى ذلك, استخدم مركبات Trident الطافية في Olympus, واحصل على أحدث Battle Pass, واصعد إلى قمة Ranked, وقم ببناء مجتمعك باستخدام الأندية. ارفع من مستوى لعبك عندما يتم إصدار الموسم 7 في 4 نوفمبر.

Apex Legends™‎ هي لعبة معارك مجانية حيث تتقاتل شخصيات أسطورية بحثًا عن المجد والشهرة والثروة على أطراف Frontier. العب مجانًا الآن على Xbox One, وPS4, وSteam, وOrigin للكمبيوتر الشخصي.

localizations.fi.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascensionin julkaisutraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Nouse uusiin korkeuksiin Apex Legendsin 7. kaudella Olympuksen leijuvassa kaupungissa. http://x.ea.com/65921

Kokonainen uusi maailma odottaa tutkimista. Olympuksessa panokset ovat kovemmat ja pudotukset vaarallisempia kuin koskaan. Uusi legenda Horizon ymmärtää tilanteen vakavuuden, ja hän on valmis antamaan muille legendoille kyytiä – halusivatpa he sitä tai eivät. Hyppää Olympuksen leijuviin Trident-autoihin, nappaa uusin Battle Pass, nouse tilastojen huipulle ja kokoa oma yhteisö Klubien avulla. Näytä taitosi, kun Season 7 käynnistyy 4. marraskuuta.

Apex Legends™ on ilmainen battle royale -peli, jossa legendaariset hahmot taistelevat maineesta, kunniasta ja mammonasta Frontierin laitamilla. Pelaa nyt ilmaiseksi Xbox Onella, PS4-järjestelmällä ja PC:llä Steamin ja Originin kautta.

localizations.ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер к выходу сезона 7 «Вознесение»
localizations.ru.description:
Достигните новых высот в сезоне 7 Apex Legends в парящем городе Олимпе.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Вашему взору открывается новый мир. На Олимпе взлеты опаснее, а падения — болезненнее. Новая легенда Хорайзон осознает всю силу тяжести положения и готова помочь другим легендам воспарить духом, хотят они того или нет. Запрыгивайте в летающий транспорт «Трезубец», берите новый боевой пропуск, устремляйтесь к вершинам рейтингового режима и создавайте свое сообщество с помощью клубов. Поднимитесь на новый уровень с началом сезона 7 уже 4 ноября.

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на Xbox One, PS4, в Steam и Origin для ПК.

localizations.pt-BR.title: Trailer de Lançamento da Temporada 7 - Ascenção de Apex Legends
localizations.pt-BR.description:
Ascenda a novas alturas na Temporada 7 de Apex Legends  na cidade voadora Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Há um mundo inteiro esperando para ser explorado. As apostas são altas e as quedas são fatais em Olympus. A nova Lenda, Horizon, entende a gravidade da situação, e ela não se importa em dar um impulso a outras Lendas, elas querendo ou não. Além disso, divirta-se com Trident, o veículo voador de Olympus, obtenha o mais novo Passe de Batalha e suba ao topo da Liga, além de construir sua comunidade com Clubes. Melhore seu jogo quando a Temporada 7 for lançada, dia 4 de novembro.

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito de battle royale em que personagens lendários lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nos limites da Fronteira. Jogue Apex Legends de graça agora no Xbox One, PlayStation®4, Steam e Origin para PC.

localizations.nl-NL.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Klim naar nieuwe hoogten tijdens Apex Legends Season 7 in de zwevende stad Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Er wacht een hele nieuwe wereld op verkenning. Op Olympus is de inzet hoger en zijn de vallen dodelijker. De nieuwe Legend Horizon begrijpt de ernst van de situatie, en zal de andere Legends zeker een ""lift"" geven: of ze nu willen of niet. Spring daarnaast op de zwevende Trident-voertuigen van Olympus, pak de nieuwste Battle Pass, klim omhoog naar de top van Ranked en bouw je community op met clubs. Verbeter je spel als Season 7 wordt uitgebracht op 4 november.

Apex Legends™ is een free-to-play battle royale-spel waarin legendarische personages strijden om glorie, roem en fortuin aan de rand van de Frontier. Speel nu gratis op de Xbox One, PS4, Steam en Origin for PC.

localizations.sv.title: Lanseringstrailer för Apex Legends Säsong 7 – Ascension
localizations.sv.description:
Stig upp till nya höjder i Apex Legends Säsong 7 i den svävande staden Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny värld väntar på bli utforskad. Mer står på spel och fallen är dödligare på Olympus. Den nya legendaren Horizon förstår tyngden i situationen och hon kommer säkert ge andra legendarer ett lyft - oavsett om de vill eller inte. Dessutom kan du hoppa på Olympus svävande Trident-fordon, hämta det senaste Battle Passet, klättra upp till toppen på Ranked och bygga en gemenskap med klubbar. Ta ditt spel till nästa nivå när Säsong 7 släpps den 4 november.

Apex Legends™ är ett gratis battle royale-spel där legendariska karaktärer strider för ära, berömmelse och rikedom på gränslandets utkanter. Spela gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam och Origin för PC.

localizations.es-MX.description:
Supera tus límites en la ciudad flotante de Olympus en la temporada 7 de Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un nuevo mundo te espera para ser explorado. En Olympus, las apuestas son más altas y las caídas más letales. Horizon, la nueva leyenda, entiende la gravedad de la situación y está preparada para darle un aventón a las demás leyendas... Lo quieran o no. Súbete a los vehículos flotantes Trident de Olympus, obtén el último Battle Pass, asciende a la cima de la clasificación y crea tu comunidad con los clubes. Mejora tu juego cuando se lance la temporada 7 el 4 de noviembre.

Apex Legends™ es un juego gratuito estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ahora en Xbox One, PS4, Steam y Origin para PC.

localizations.da.title: Apex Legends sæson 7 – lanceringstrailer for Ascension
localizations.da.description:
Nå nye højder i Apex Legends sæson 7 på den svævende by Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden, der bare venter på at blive udforsket. Der er endnu mere på spil og endnu dybere at falde på Olympus. Den nye legende Horizon har forstået situationens alvor, og skal nok give de andre legender et løft – om de vil det eller ej. Desuden kan du hoppe på Olympus' svævende Trident-fartøjer, snuppe det nyeste Battle Pass, nå til tops i Ranked og skabe et fællesskab med klubber. Sæt trumf på dit spil, når sæson 7 udkommer 4. november.

Apex Legends™ er et gratis Battle Royale-spil, hvor legendariske figurer kæmper om hæder, berømmelse og held i grænseområdet. Spil gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam og Origin til pc.

Produtor: Matheus Portugal

[LETRA]
PL Quest
Eu quase nunca sou de arruma problema
Mas meu bonde quase aqui não tem pena
Se der mole o Botafogo te acerta
Não me estressa que eu to sem paciência

Me tira pra lok cabelinho de trança
Essa Porraa é disfarce então não pangua
Barberinho que já deixo na régua
Vulgo nas costa camisa da França

Sueth
Ela joga a bunda e não para
me viu no baile com duas glockada
Me viu no baile com duas namorada
Na onda do lança e bebendo bala

PL Quest
Me tira pra lok cabelinho de trança
Essa Porraa é disfarce então não pangua
Barberinho que já deixo na régua
Vulgo nas costa camisa da França

Sueth
Camisa da França no baile da China
Pela chumbada fumando erva fina
Igual zona sul são várias patricinha
Jogando firme pros mano da firma

Me tira pra lok de cabelo branco
Se eu to com o porte quem deixo foi o mano
Me avista no baile ela fica jogando
Água dos amigo é só cavalo branco

PL Quest
Hoje tem baile da China
Várias droga várias linda
Parecer camarim de artista
Baile rola até meio dia

Clario eu jogo a lupa na vista
Se eu to com vontade de ir no banheiro
Quem abre o caminho é o amigo do AK
O lança na mão e o copao na outra
O baile tá cheio mas não me esbarra

Ela joga a bunda e não para
me viu no baile com duas glockada
Me viu no baile com duas namorada
Na onda do lança e bebendo bala

PL Quest
Me tira pra lok cabelinho de trança
Essa Porraa é disfarce então não pangua
Barberinho que já deixo na régua
Vulgo nas costa camisa da França

Sueth
Dia de baile com o pente de 30
Ela passa e repara a camisa
Ela passa já chama as amiga
Rende pra nós porque nós é artista

PL Quest
Nunca vai entender porque eu tenho dinheiro
ainda mais que eu sou um jovem negro
Esses branco nunca vai me por medo
Alforria para um Jovem preto

me viu no baile com duas glockada
Me viu no baile com duas namorada

snippet.title: Novo Nissan Versa 2021 | Sense, a Versão com Melhor Custo Benefício!
snippet.description:
Novo Versa 2021 chega com visual totalmente novo e com bom nível de segurança. O Novo Nissan Versa tem plataforma e motor de Kicks. Sai equipado com motor 1.6 de 114 cv em todas as versões. Veja o preço abaixo e confira todos os detalhes com Giu Brandão.

PREÇO

Versa Sense 1.6 Manual – R$ 72.990
Versa Sense 1.6 CVT – R$ 77.990
Versa Advance 1.6 CVT – R$ 83.490
Versa Exclusive 1.6 CVT – R$ 92.990

8 CORES

Preto Premium - Sólida
Branco Aspen -Sólida
Prata Classic - Metálica
Cinza grafite - Metálica
Vermelho Malbec - Metálica
Vermelho Scarlet - Metálica (Exclusive)
Branco Diamond - Perolizada
Azul Cobalto - Perolizada
 
EQUIPAMENTOS VERSA 2021

Versa Sense 1.6 16V Manual – R$ 72.990
- Acabamento de tecido nos bancos 
- Ar-condicionado
- Comandos de áudio e telefone no volante
- Chave inteligente presencial (I-Key)
- Sistema eletrônico de ignição (botão Push Start)
- Painel central com tela de 3,5 polegadas
- Retrovisores externos com regulagem elétrica
- Rodas de aço aro 15 com calotas integrais
- Airbags duplos frontais
- Airbags laterais e de cortina
- Alerta de cinto de segurança destravado (frontal e traseiros)
- Controle de Tração e Estabilidade (VDC)
- Fixadores traseiros para cadeiras de crianças (Isofix)
- Freios ABS com controle eletrônico de frenagem (EBD) e assistência de frenagem (BA)
- Sensor de estacionamento traseiro
- Sistema Inteligente de Partida em Rampa (HSA)
- Sistema de áudio com rádio AM/FM, entrada auxiliar, conector USB (3 um no painel e dois no console para passageiros do banco traseiro)

Versa Sense 1.6 16V CVT – R$ 77.990
Todos os itens da versão Sense com câmbio manual mais:
- Câmbio XTRONIC® CVT com função Overdrive
- Apoio de braço frontal
- Controle automático de velocidade com comando no volante

Versa Advance 1.6 16V CVT – R$ 83.490
Todos os itens da versão Sense CVT mais:
- Acendimento inteligente dos faróis
- Banco traseiro bipartido rebatível (60/40)
- Faróis com função Follow Me Home
- Indicador de temperatura externa
- Painel central multifuncional em TFT de 7 polegadas com 12 funções
- Retrovisores externos com indicadores de direção
- Rodas de liga leve aro 16
 - Câmera traseira de estacionamento 
- Faróis de neblina
- Alerta de Objetos no Banco Traseiro (Rear Door Alert)
- Multimídia com tela de toque colorida de 7”, Apple CarPlay, Android Auto, Bluetooth, compatível com aplicativo Nissan Smart Phone

Versa Exclusive 1.6 16V CVT – R$ 92.990
Todos os itens da versão Advance CVT mais:
- Acabamento premium soft touch nos bancos 
- Ar-condicionado automático digital
- Apoio de braço central traseiro
- Welcome Function
- Volantes com acabamento premium soft touch
- Antena estilo barbatana de tubarão
- Faróis dianteiros em LED
- Assinatura dos faróis dianteiros em LED
- Rodas de liga leve aro 17
- Alerta de Colisão Frontal com Assistente Inteligente de Frenagem (FCW/FEB)
- Visão 360° Inteligente com imagem integrada à tela do rádio 
- Detector de Objetos em Movimento (MOD)
- Alerta de Tráfego Cruzado Traseiro (RCTA)
- Monitoramento de Ponto Cego (BSW) 
- Espelho retrovisor com aquecimento 
- 2 tweeters
- GPS integrado

CONSUMO

- VERSA 1.6 MANUAL

Cidade: 8,1 Km/l (E) 11,8 Km/l (G)
Estrada: 9,6 Km/l (E) 13,8 Km/l (G)

- VERSA 1.6 AUTOMÁTICO 

Cidade: 8,0 Km/l (E) 11,7 Km/l (G)  
Estrada: 10,0 Km/l (E) 13,9 Km/l (G)  

FICHA TÉCNICA

NOVO NISSAN VERSA 1.6 MANUAL 2021

Motor: 1.6 aspirado flex, 16V, 4 cilindros, acelerador eletrônico   
Potência: 114 cv @ 5.600 rpm (G/E)
Torque: 15,5 kgfm @ 4.000 rpm (G/E)
0 @ 100 km/h: 185 km/h
Velocidade máxima: 10,8 segundos
Câmbio: Manual de 5 marchas ou autoático CVT 
Tração: Dianteira
Direção: Elétrica com assistência variável
Raio de giro: 5,30 m    
Batente a Batente: 2,64 voltas 
Suspensão: McPherson (diant.) e eixo de torção (tras.)
Freios: Discos ventilados (diant.) e sólidos (tras.)
Pneus e rodas: 195/65 R15 na Sense | 205/55 R16 na Advance | 205/50 R17 na Exclusive
Tamanho: 4,49 m de comprimento / 1,74 m de largura / 1,47 m de altura (vazio)
Entre-eixos: 2,62 m
Vão livre: 13,8 cm (Sense e Advance) e 14,3 cm (Exclusive)
Tanque: 41 litros
Porta-malas: 466 litros (Sense) e 482 litros (Advance e Exclusive)
Peso em ordem de marcha: 1.074,0kg (Sense) e 1.131 kg (Exclusive)
Peso Total: 1.532 kg (manual) e 1.644 kg (CVT)
Capacidade de carga: 513 kg (Exclusive)
Ângulo de ataque: 16,4° (Sense) / 16,9° (Exclusive)
Ângulo de saída: 19,9° (Sense) / 20,2° (Exclusive)
Revisão: 10 mil km ou 12 meses   
Garantia: 3 anos (sem limite de quilometragem)  
Assistência 24 horas: 2 anos

==============================

snippet.title: Tudo sobre ATHLÉTICO PARANAENSE X FLAMENGO
snippet.description:
A quarta-feira será dia de estreia na Copa do Brasil de 2020 para o Athletico, atual campeão do torneio, e o Flamengo, defensor do título da Libertadores e do Brasileirão nesta temporada. O encontro entre os rubro-negros do Paraná e do Rio de Janeiro, pelas oitavas de final da Copa do Brasil, será na Arena da Baixada, a partir das 21h30.

Transmissão: TV Globo com narração de Luis Roberto e comentários de Júnior e Roger Flores. SporTV2 com narração de Gustavo Villani e comentários de Lédio Carmona e Grafite.

Quem mora fora do Brasil pode acompanhar ao vivo e com imagens pelo site oficial da copa do Brasil

snippet.title: Phrenologie stimmt nie
snippet.description:
… außer rein zufällig :)
Eine kürzlich veröffentlichte Studie schlägt Wellen: mit Hilfe von Machine Learning soll man jemandem am Gesicht ablesen können, wie vertrauenswürdig sie oder er ist. Phrenologie! Lautet der Vorwurf - eine Pseudowissenschaft, nach welcher sich Persönlichkeiten an der Kopfform ablesen lassen sollen und die in der Geschichte oft zur “wissenschaftlichen” Rechtfertigung von Diskriminierung benutzt wurde. Doch ein genauerer Blick lohnt sich…(für alle alten Freunde der Sonne - das hier ist Journal Club Deluxe :))

INHALT
0:00 Drama um Studie - Phrenologievorwurf
1:29 Was ist Phrenologie?
8:02 Das Studiendesign / Machine Learning
10:38 Das eigentliche Problem mit dieser Studie
15:05 Keksempfehlungen

maiLab wird produziert von Mai Thi Nguyen-Kim für funk (ARD & ZDF)
►funk Web-App: https://go.funk.net  
►https://go.funk.net/impressum 


QUELLEN

Die Studie, um die es geht: ein Algorithmus, der historische Gemälde nach ihrer wahrgenommenen Vertrauenswürdigkeit zuordnen soll: https://www.nature.com/articles/s41467-020-18566-7

Ein Artikel zu der Studie im britischen Boulevardblatt The Sun: https://bit.ly/3mu2a9O 

Gute Übersichten zu Phrenologie & Franz Joseph Gall: 
https://bit.ly/3jDflmT
https://bit.ly/2TwFKbk 

Zu den verschiedenen Aufgaben der Amygdala (die man normalerweise vor allem als Angstzentrum kennenlernt) gehören auch: emotionales Lernen und Gedächtnis (https://bit.ly/2TLEn9b), Verarbeitung von Belohnung und Strafe (https://go.nature.com/2TC9y6o), Einschätzung der Vertrauenswürdigkeit von Gesichtern (https://bit.ly/37RtlYe). 

Für den Kunstsinn kommt es nicht auf eine einzelne Region an, sondern es ist das Zusammenspiel verschiedener Regionen, das sich bei Künstlern und Nicht-Künstlern unterscheidet: https://go.nature.com/3kQDhF3 

Ein relativ aktueller Artikel, der im Video nicht genannt wird, gibt ebenfalls einen schönen Einblick: ein “Schönheitszentrum” in dem Sinn gibt es nicht im Gehirn. Die Schönheit von Gesichtern und die Schönheit von Kunst werden in Regionen verarbeitet, die sich nicht überschneiden. https://bit.ly/3mwxrsO 

Ein Teil des Hippocampus ist größer bei Taxifahrern als bei Busfahrern: https://bit.ly/2TwHeSW. Da diese Region auch für das Ortsgedächtnis zuständig ist, wird dieser Unterschied als Nachweis dafür gesehen, dass zumindest in manchen Fällen die Form des Gehirns tatsächlich mit bestimmten Eigenschaften in Verbindung steht.

Allerdings: eine große Studie mit MRT-Daten von Tausenden Personen findet keine von der Phrenologie beschriebenen Zusammenhänge. Dazu kommt, dass die Form des Kortex generell nur sehr wenig mit der das Schädels zusammenhängt: https://bit.ly/35GkuWt 

Studie zu Machine Learning, bei der festgestellt wurde, dass der Algorithmus menschliche Finger als Identifikationsmerkmal von Schleien benutzt hat (siehe Figure 3, obere Reihe): https://bit.ly/2G6TB5a 

Wie vertrauenswürdig wir ein Gesicht finden hängt auch davon ab, wie attraktiv wir es finden. Dieser Zusammenhang ist sehr stark: je nach Art und Intensität der ausgedrückten Emotion kann diese Korrelation eine Stärke von bis zu r = 0.90 haben. https://bit.ly/2G8poTt 

Es gibt immer wieder Studien, die berichten, dass man beim Menschen eben doch die Persönlichkeit am Gesicht ablesen könnte. Aber es gibt versch. Gründe für Zweifel, z.B. dass die Persönlichkeit des Betrachters eine Rolle spielt (https://bit.ly/3oENFlA) und dass sich Dinge wie Frisur, Kleidung etc. (bei Alltagsfotos) auf die Bewertung niederschlagen (https://go.nature.com/3jz5GOp). Aber auch bei standardisierten Gesichtern gibt es Fallstricke: so wirkt ein maskulineres Gesicht in der Persönlichkeit dominanter und stabiler, unabhängig davon ob die Person das wirklich ist (https://bit.ly/3mv8Wfj). 
Zu einem gewissen Maß ging in einer Studie aggressives Verhalten bei Eishockeyspielern mit einem breiten Gesicht einher (https://bit.ly/37MSZgA). Die Idee: ein höherer Testosteronlevel führt zu einem breiteren Gesicht (https://bit.ly/3oBe3wr) und fördert auch (in sehr schwachem Maß beim Menschen) aggressives Verhalten (https://bit.ly/31RicT4). Allerdings sind beide Zusammenhänge wenig verlässlich, da unsere Aggressionslevels im Alltag meist von anderen Dingen abhängen: der Korrelationskoeffizient liegt bei dem sehr geringen Wert von r = 0.08.

BILDQUELLEN

Phrenologie

Von Elya, CC BY-SA 3.0, https://commons.wikimedia.org/w/index.php?curid=23991387

snippet.title: Corona-Gipfel: Wie hart werden die Maßnahmen? I ZDFheute live
snippet.description:
Kommen neue Kontaktbeschränkungen - und machen Restaurant wieder dicht? Bund und Länder beraten über schärfere Corona-Maßnahmen.

Wir begleiten die Pressekonferenz von Bundeskanzlerin Angela Merkel und den Ministerpräsident*innen live. Mit unserer Hauptstadt-Korrespondentin Nicole Diekmann ordnen wir die Ergebnisse ein. Diskutiert mit und stellt eure Fragen! 



Die Bundesregierung schätzt die Lage ernst ein. Wirtschaftsminister Peter Altmaier (CDU) rechnet schon am Ende dieser Woche mit 20.000 Neuinfektionen am Tag.  Bei den Beratungen von Bund und Ländern dürften diese Fragen im Mittelpunkt stehen: Wirken die Maßnahmen? Würde ein kurzer, zeitlich beschränkter Shutdown mehr bringen als ein längerer, der nicht ganz so streng ausfällt? Wäre ein sogenannter "Wellenbrecher-Lockdown" verhältnismäßig?


----- 
Hier auf ZDFheute Nachrichten erfahrt ihr, was auf der Welt passiert und was uns alle etwas angeht: Wir sorgen für Durchblick in der Nachrichtenwelt, erklären die Hintergründe und gehen auf gesellschaftliche Debatten ein. Diskutiert in Livestreams mit uns und bildet euch eure eigene Meinung mit den Fakten, die wir euch präsentieren.

Abonniert unseren Kanal, um nichts mehr zu verpassen.

Immer auf dem aktuellen Stand seid ihr auf http://www.ZDFheute.de/.
#Merkel #Corona

snippet.title: OMG! 😱 DAS passiert bei der Hochzeit!!! 💔😨  | Köln 50667 #1981
snippet.description:
Lea kann sich nicht mehr länger halten, als Cora mit Absicht ihr Brautkleid schmutzig macht und so kommt es vor Bens Augen zu einem Kampf der Giganten. Zu Leas Pech schleudert sie in diesem Cora entgegen, dass sie nur aus Eifersucht den Antrag gemacht hätte. Wie wird Ben auf die Aussage reagieren? 

Abonniert unseren Kanal: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCnrvUg5MJWPDSrv_voT7AqA?sub_confirmation=1
Instagram: http://www.instagram.com/koeln50667
Schaut euch die kompletten Folgen auf TVNOW an: http://www.tvnow.de/rtl2/koeln-50667
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/koeln50667
Twitter: http://twitter.com/rtl2

„Köln 50667“ ist eine Reality-Soap, die seit 2013 täglich von montags bis freitags im Vorabendprogramm gesendet wird. Aufgrund des großen Erfolges wurde die ursprünglich auf 120 Folgen begrenzte Serie weiter produziert und ist bisher auf über 1700 Folgen angewachsen. Im Mittelpunkt stehen unter anderem Kevin, Jan, Sophia, Marc und Mel. "Köln 50667" erzählt die spannenden Geschichten von Kevin, Sophia und Co. Egal, ob im Cage oder in den WGs - hier gibt es Leben pur.

snippet.title: Neue Corona-Maßnahmen: Darf der Staat das überhaupt? | #analyse
snippet.description:
Deutschland wird wieder teilweise heruntergefahren: Ab dem 2. November müssen Restaurants und Kneipen schließen, es gelten neue Kontaktbeschränkungen - und Sportveranstaltungen dürfen nur ohne Zuschauer stattfinden. Es sind erneut tiefe Eingriffe in unseren Alltag. Darf die Politik so etwas überhaupt entscheiden? Wo sind die Grenzen? Und: Was sagen die Gerichte?

Aktuelle Hintergründe zu den Maßnahmen erfahrt ihr im "Corona-Blog" des ZDF - https://www.zdf.de/nachrichten/politik/blog-coronavirus-102.html

Auch die Bundesregierung informiert auf ihrer Website über deutschlandweite Maßnahmen - https://www.bundesregierung.de/breg-de/themen/coronavirus/corona-massnahmen-1734724

Information zur Belegung von Intensivbetten - https://www.intensivregister.de/#/index

Das "Infektionsschutzgesetz" - https://www.gesetze-im-internet.de/ifsg

Wie weit dürfen Grundrechtseinschränkungen gehen? Ein Interview mit der Juristin Anika Klafki - https://www.bpb.de/politik/innenpolitik/coronavirus/307395/grundrechte

... und ein weiteres Interview zu diesem Thema mit der Juristin Dagmar Felix - https://www.uni-hamburg.de/newsroom/im-fokus/2020/0312-corona-regierung-reaktion.html

 Mein Kanal gehört zu funk, dem Netzwerk von ARD und ZDF. Weitere Infos:

snippet.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Rise to new heights in Apex Legends Season 7 on the floating city of Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

There’s a whole new world waiting to be explored. The stakes are higher and the falls are deadlier on Olympus. New Legend Horizon understands the gravity of the situation, and she’s sure to give the other Legends a lift -- whether they want it or not. Plus hop on Olympus’s floating Trident vehicles, grab the latest Battle Pass, ascend to the top of Ranked, and build your community with Clubs. Up your game when Season 7 releases on November 4.

Apex Legends™ is a free-to-play battle royale game where legendary characters battle for glory, fame, and fortune on the fringes of the Frontier. Play for free now on Xbox One, PS4, and Origin for PC. And play on Steam when Season 7 launches on November 4 !  

Learn more about Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension: http://x.ea.com/65921
 
Check out our YouTube channel: http://x.ea.com/56710.
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/playapex.
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/playapex/.

localizations.de-DE.title: Apex Legends Saison 7 – Aufstieg-Launch-Trailer
localizations.de-DE.description:
Starte deinen Höhenflug in Apex Legends Saison 7 auf der schwebenden Stadt Olympus  http://x.ea.com/65921

Erkunde eine völlig neue Welt. Auf Olympus ist der Einsatz höher und jeder Sturz noch tödlicher. Die neue Legende, Horizon, weiß um den Ernst der Lage und hilft den anderen Legenden auf die Sprünge – ob sie wollen oder nicht. Drehe auf Olympus außerdem eine Runde mit den schwebenden Tridents, hol dir den neuesten Battle Pass, klettere an die Spitze der Rangliste und baue mit Clubs deine eigene Community auf. Bringe dein Spiel voran, wenn Saison 7 am 5. November erscheint.

Apex Legends™ ist ein Free-to-Play-Battle-Royale-Spiel, bei dem legendäre Charaktere am Rande des Grenzlands um Ruhm und Reichtum kämpfen. Jetzt kostenlos auf Xbox One, PS4 sowie Steam und Origin für PC spielen.

localizations.pt-PT.title: Apex Legends Temporada 7 – Trailer de Lançamento de Ascension
localizations.pt-PT.description:
Sobe a novas alturas na cidade flutuante de Olympus com a Temporada 7 de Apex Legends  http://x.ea.com/65921

Há um mundo à espera de ser explorado. Em Olympus, o risco é grande e as quedas são ainda maiores. Horizon, a nova Lenda, compreende a gravidade da situação e está pronta para dar um empurrãozinho aos seus adversários, quer eles queiram quer não... Podes ainda sentar-te ao volante dos veículos flutuantes Trident, agarrar o mais recente Battle Pass, atingir o topo da classificação e contribuir para a comunidade com os Clubs. Melhora o teu jogo a 4 de novembro com o arranque da Temporada 7.

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito do género battle royale onde personagens lendárias lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nas periferias da Fronteira. Joga já de graça na Xbox One, PS4, Steam e Origin para PC.

localizations.fr-FR.title: Trailer de lancement de la saison 7 d’Apex Legends - Ascension
localizations.fr-FR.description:
Atteignez de nouveaux sommets pendant la saison 7 d'Apex Legends en explorant la ville flottante d'Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Explorez un tout nouveau monde. À Olympus, les enjeux sont de taille et les chutes mortelles. La nouvelle Légende Horizon est consciente de la gravité de la situation et compte se faire entendre auprès des autres Légendes, que ce soit de gré ou de force. Découvrez le Trident, un aéroglisseur qui vous aidera à traverser Olympus à toute vitesse, obtenez le nouveau Passe de combat, progressez dans les ligues classées et développez votre communauté grâce au système de clubs. Préparez-vous pour la saison 7, qui débutera le 4 novembre.

Apex Legends™ est un jeu de tir Battle Royale Free-to-Play où des personnages légendaires combattent ensemble aux confins de la Frontière pour la gloire et la fortune. Jouez gratuitement sur PlayStation 4, Xbox One et Steam ou Origin pour PC.

localizations.no.title: Apex Legends – Sesong 7 – Ascension-lanseringstrailer
localizations.no.description:
Nå nye høyder i den 7. sesongen av Apex Legends, som finner sted i den svevende byen Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden venter på å bli utforsket. Enda mer står på spill og høydene blir enda farligere på Olympus. Den nye legenden Horizon forstår byrden situasjonen byr på, og hun kan gi de andre legendene et løft – enten de vil det eller ei. Hopp ombord i de svevende Trident-kjøretøyene på Olympus, skaff deg spillets nye Battle Pass, nå toppen i rangerte kamper og etabler ditt eget fellesskap med klubber. Ta spillet til nye høyder når sesong 7 lanseres 4. november.

Apex Legends™ er et gratis battle royale-spill hvor legendariske karakterer kjemper om rikdom og ære i utkanten av grenselandet. Spill gratis på Xbox One, PS4 og Steam og Origin for PC nå.

localizations.it.title: Apex Legends - Stagione 7 - Ascensione - Il trailer di lancio
localizations.it.description:
Raggiungi nuove vette ed esplora la città sospesa di Olympus nella Stagione 7 di Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un mondo inesplorato ti aspetta. A Olympus, il pericolo è sempre in agguato e gli errori non lasciano scampo. La nuova leggenda Horizon conosce la... gravità della situazione ed è pronta a tirare su le altre leggende, che lo vogliano o meno. Usa i Trident per spostarti in giro per la mappa, ottieni il nuovo pass battaglia, scala le vette della competizione nella modalità Classificata e crea la tua community con i club. Dai il massimo nella Stagione 7, in arrivo il 4 novembre.

Apex Legends™ è un gioco gratuito in stile battle royale in cui personaggi leggendari si sfidano per gloria, fama e ricchezza ai margini della Frontiera. Gioca gratis su Xbox One, PlayStation 4, e Steam e Origin per PC.

localizations.pl.title: Zwiastun sezonu 7. Apex Legends: Wstąpienie
localizations.pl.description:
Wznies się na wyżyny w 7. sezonie Apex Legends w latającym mieście Olimp.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Nowy świat czeka na odkrycie. Na Olimpie stawki są większe, a upadki bardziej bolesne. Nowa legenda, Horizon, dobrze zdaje sobie sprawę z wagi sytuacji i chętnie pomoże pozostałym legendom – czy tego chcą, czy nie. Wsiądźcie do latających pojazdów Olimpu, Trójzębów, i sprawcie sobie nową przepustkę bojową, pnijcie się na szczyt rankingu i rozwijajcie społeczność w Klubach. Pozwól rozgrywce wstąpić na wyższy poziom z premierą 7. sezonu już 4 listopada.

Apex Legends™ to darmowa gra Battle Royale, w której legendarne postacie mierzą się ze sobą w walce o sławę i chwałę na obrzeżach Kresów. Graj w Apex Legends za darmo już teraz – na Xbox One, PlayStation 4, Steam oraz Origin na PC.

localizations.ja.title: 「エーペックスレジェンズ シーズン7 – アセンション」ローンチトレーラー
localizations.ja.description:
空中都市オリンパスへ向かい、「エーペックスレジェンズ」シーズン7で新たな高みを目指せ。http://x.ea.com/65921

まったく新しい未知の世界が広がる。オリンパスはこれまで以上の危険をはらみ、落下の影響はこれまでの比ではない。新レジェンドのホライゾンはその重大性を認識し、重力を熟知する存在。他のレジェンドが望むと望まざるに関わらず、空中へと巻き上げてしまう。オリンパスでは飛行型ビークル「トライデント」に乗り込み、バトルパスを手にしてランクシリーズの上位を目指そう。新登場の「クラブ」機能を使って自身のコミュニティを作ることも可能だ。11月4日、シーズン7で高みを目指せ。

「エーペックスレジェンズ™」は、伝説の戦士が集結してフロンティアの辺境で富と栄誉と名声を懸けて戦う、基本プレイ無料のバトルロイヤル作品。Xbox One、PS4、Steam、Origin（PC）で今すぐ無料プレイ。

localizations.zh-Hans.description:
参加《Apex Legends》第 7 赛季，光临漂浮城市“奥林匹斯”，达到全新高度。http://x.ea.com/65921

有一个全新的世界等着我们去探索。奥林匹斯这里赌注更大，而致命程度也更高。全新传奇地平线，她了解引力，而且能让其他传奇悬浮──无论他们愿不愿意。跳上奥林匹斯的“三叉戟”漂浮载具，入手最新的战斗通行证，登上排位赛之巅，并以“俱乐部”来组建你的社区。就在 11 月 4 日第 7 赛季推出时大显身手。

《Apex Legends™》是一款免费大逃杀游戏，传奇角色们在边境边缘为荣誉、名望和财富而战。赶快在 Xbox One、PS4 和 PC 端 Steam 与 Origin 上免费游玩。

localizations.zh-Hant.description:
在《Apex 英雄》賽季 7 的漂浮城市「奧林匹斯」中達到新高度。 http://x.ea.com/65921

一個全新的世界等你來探索。在奧林匹斯這裡賭注更大，而致命程度也更高。新英雄天際線，她了解引力，而且能讓其他英雄懸浮──無論他們願不願意。另外，登上奧林匹斯的懸浮「三叉戟」載具、取得最新的戰鬥通行證、提升積分排名，並使用「俱樂部」打造你的社群。就在 11 月 4 日賽季 7 推出時大顯身手。

《Apex 英雄》是一款可免費遊玩的大逃殺遊戲，傳說中的角色們將在邊境的遠處，為榮耀、名聲與財富而戰。立即在 Xbox One、PS4、PC Origin 與 Steam 上免費遊玩。

localizations.ko.title: Apex 레전드 시즌 7 – 어센션 출시 트레일러
localizations.ko.description:
Apex 레전드 시즌 7에서 새로운 천공의 도시 올림푸스로 떠오르십시오.  http://x.ea.com/65921

완전히 새로운 세계를 탐험하십시오. 높은 고도의 올림푸스에서는 위험도 더 커집니다. 신규 레전드 호라이즌은 중력만큼이나 중대한 상황을 이해하며, 다른 레전드를 높이 띄워 줍니다. 원하지 않더라도 말이죠. 올림푸스의 부양 트라이던트 차량에 타보고, 최신 배틀 패스를 손에 넣고 랭크의 최상위로 뛰어오르며 클럽을 만들어 공동체를 운영하십시오. 11월 4일 시즌7으로 게임의 수준을 한층 더 높이십시오.

Apex 레전드™는 전설적인 캐릭터들이 영광과 명성, 부를 쟁취하기 위해 프런티어의 변경에서 치열한 전투를 벌이는 부분 유료 배틀 로얄 게임입니다. Xbox One, PlayStation 4 및 PC용 Steam 및 Origin에서 Apex 레전드를 무료 플레이하십시오.

localizations.ar.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – إعلان طرح Ascension
localizations.ar.description:
ارتق إلى مستويات جديدة في الموسم 7 من Apex Legends في مدينة Olympus الطافية.  http://x.ea.com/65921

هنالك عالم جديد بالكامل في انتظارك لكي تستكشفه. إن المخاطر عالية والإخفاقات أشد فتكًا في Olympus. الأسطورة الجديدة Horizon تعي خطورة الموقف, وسوف تحرص على تقديم المساعدة للجميع, سواء أرادوا ذلك أم لا. بالإضافة إلى ذلك, استخدم مركبات Trident الطافية في Olympus, واحصل على أحدث Battle Pass, واصعد إلى قمة Ranked, وقم ببناء مجتمعك باستخدام الأندية. ارفع من مستوى لعبك عندما يتم إصدار الموسم 7 في 4 نوفمبر.

Apex Legends™‎ هي لعبة معارك مجانية حيث تتقاتل شخصيات أسطورية بحثًا عن المجد والشهرة والثروة على أطراف Frontier. العب مجانًا الآن على Xbox One, وPS4, وSteam, وOrigin للكمبيوتر الشخصي.

localizations.fi.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascensionin julkaisutraileri
localizations.fi.description:
Nouse uusiin korkeuksiin Apex Legendsin 7. kaudella Olympuksen leijuvassa kaupungissa. http://x.ea.com/65921

Kokonainen uusi maailma odottaa tutkimista. Olympuksessa panokset ovat kovemmat ja pudotukset vaarallisempia kuin koskaan. Uusi legenda Horizon ymmärtää tilanteen vakavuuden, ja hän on valmis antamaan muille legendoille kyytiä – halusivatpa he sitä tai eivät. Hyppää Olympuksen leijuviin Trident-autoihin, nappaa uusin Battle Pass, nouse tilastojen huipulle ja kokoa oma yhteisö Klubien avulla. Näytä taitosi, kun Season 7 käynnistyy 4. marraskuuta.

Apex Legends™ on ilmainen battle royale -peli, jossa legendaariset hahmot taistelevat maineesta, kunniasta ja mammonasta Frontierin laitamilla. Pelaa nyt ilmaiseksi Xbox Onella, PS4-järjestelmällä ja PC:llä Steamin ja Originin kautta.

localizations.ru.title: Apex Legends — трейлер к выходу сезона 7 «Вознесение»
localizations.ru.description:
Достигните новых высот в сезоне 7 Apex Legends в парящем городе Олимпе.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Вашему взору открывается новый мир. На Олимпе взлеты опаснее, а падения — болезненнее. Новая легенда Хорайзон осознает всю силу тяжести положения и готова помочь другим легендам воспарить духом, хотят они того или нет. Запрыгивайте в летающий транспорт «Трезубец», берите новый боевой пропуск, устремляйтесь к вершинам рейтингового режима и создавайте свое сообщество с помощью клубов. Поднимитесь на новый уровень с началом сезона 7 уже 4 ноября.

Apex Legends™ — бесплатная игра в жанре «королевская битва», где легендарные персонажи сражаются за славу и богатства на дальних рубежах Фронтира. Играйте бесплатно на Xbox One, PS4, в Steam и Origin для ПК.

localizations.pt-BR.title: Trailer de Lançamento da Temporada 7 - Ascenção de Apex Legends
localizations.pt-BR.description:
Ascenda a novas alturas na Temporada 7 de Apex Legends  na cidade voadora Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Há um mundo inteiro esperando para ser explorado. As apostas são altas e as quedas são fatais em Olympus. A nova Lenda, Horizon, entende a gravidade da situação, e ela não se importa em dar um impulso a outras Lendas, elas querendo ou não. Além disso, divirta-se com Trident, o veículo voador de Olympus, obtenha o mais novo Passe de Batalha e suba ao topo da Liga, além de construir sua comunidade com Clubes. Melhore seu jogo quando a Temporada 7 for lançada, dia 4 de novembro.

Apex Legends™ é um jogo gratuito de battle royale em que personagens lendários lutam por glória, fama e fortuna nos limites da Fronteira. Jogue Apex Legends de graça agora no Xbox One, PlayStation®4, Steam e Origin para PC.

localizations.nl-NL.title: Apex Legends Season 7 – Ascension Launch Trailer
localizations.nl-NL.description:
Klim naar nieuwe hoogten tijdens Apex Legends Season 7 in de zwevende stad Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Er wacht een hele nieuwe wereld op verkenning. Op Olympus is de inzet hoger en zijn de vallen dodelijker. De nieuwe Legend Horizon begrijpt de ernst van de situatie, en zal de andere Legends zeker een ""lift"" geven: of ze nu willen of niet. Spring daarnaast op de zwevende Trident-voertuigen van Olympus, pak de nieuwste Battle Pass, klim omhoog naar de top van Ranked en bouw je community op met clubs. Verbeter je spel als Season 7 wordt uitgebracht op 4 november.

Apex Legends™ is een free-to-play battle royale-spel waarin legendarische personages strijden om glorie, roem en fortuin aan de rand van de Frontier. Speel nu gratis op de Xbox One, PS4, Steam en Origin for PC.

localizations.sv.title: Lanseringstrailer för Apex Legends Säsong 7 – Ascension
localizations.sv.description:
Stig upp till nya höjder i Apex Legends Säsong 7 i den svävande staden Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny värld väntar på bli utforskad. Mer står på spel och fallen är dödligare på Olympus. Den nya legendaren Horizon förstår tyngden i situationen och hon kommer säkert ge andra legendarer ett lyft - oavsett om de vill eller inte. Dessutom kan du hoppa på Olympus svävande Trident-fordon, hämta det senaste Battle Passet, klättra upp till toppen på Ranked och bygga en gemenskap med klubbar. Ta ditt spel till nästa nivå när Säsong 7 släpps den 4 november.

Apex Legends™ är ett gratis battle royale-spel där legendariska karaktärer strider för ära, berömmelse och rikedom på gränslandets utkanter. Spela gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam och Origin för PC.

localizations.es-MX.description:
Supera tus límites en la ciudad flotante de Olympus en la temporada 7 de Apex Legends.  http://x.ea.com/65921

Un nuevo mundo te espera para ser explorado. En Olympus, las apuestas son más altas y las caídas más letales. Horizon, la nueva leyenda, entiende la gravedad de la situación y está preparada para darle un aventón a las demás leyendas... Lo quieran o no. Súbete a los vehículos flotantes Trident de Olympus, obtén el último Battle Pass, asciende a la cima de la clasificación y crea tu comunidad con los clubes. Mejora tu juego cuando se lance la temporada 7 el 4 de noviembre.

Apex Legends™ es un juego gratuito estilo Battle Royale en el que personajes legendarios luchan por la gloria, la fama y la fortuna en los confines de la Frontera. Juega gratis ahora en Xbox One, PS4, Steam y Origin para PC.

localizations.da.description:
Nå nye højder i Apex Legends sæson 7 på den svævende by Olympus.  http://x.ea.com/65921

En helt ny verden, der bare venter på at blive udforsket. Der er endnu mere på spil og endnu dybere at falde på Olympus. Den nye legende Horizon har forstået situationens alvor, og skal nok give de andre legender et løft – om de vil det eller ej. Desuden kan du hoppe på Olympus' svævende Trident-fartøjer, snuppe det nyeste Battle Pass, nå til tops i Ranked og skabe et fællesskab med klubber. Sæt trumf på dit spil, når sæson 7 udkommer 4. november.

Apex Legends™ er et gratis Battle Royale-spil, hvor legendariske figurer kæmper om hæder, berømmelse og held i grænseområdet. Spil gratis nu på Xbox One, PS4, Steam og Origin til pc.

snippet.title: Lebensgefährlicher Einsatz! Polizisten auf der Wache in Gefahr! | Auf Streife | SAT.1
snippet.description:
Ein Bandenchef wird festgenommen und auf die Wache Köln gebracht. Nun soll er von Jonas Schmidt erkennungsdienstlich behandelt werden. Hierbei muss er vorsorglich seine Waffen wegschließen. 
Doch was sich dann ereignet ist unglaublich! Marc Westerhoven muss schnell handeln!

#Polizei #AufStreife #Lebensgefährlichereinsatz

Immer #AufStreife - Der Polizei-Alltag ist hart und oft gefährlich.
Die Polizisten sind immer im Einsatz: Tag und Nacht, zwischen Touristen und Obdachlosen, in Villenvierteln und Problemkiezen. Auf Basis echter Fälle wird gezeigt, wie ihr Alltag aussieht: mal skurril oder gefährlich, mal amüsant oder emotional - kein Einsatz ist wie der andere! Die Beamten müssen alles geben, um sich und andere zu schützen. 

#Polizei #Polizisten #PaulRichter #StephanSindera

snippet.description:

snippet.title: „Lockdown light“ bis Ende November: Merkel fordert „nationale Kraftanstrengung"
snippet.description:
Bundeskanzlerin Angela Merkel fordert für November im Kampf gegen das Coronavirus eine „nationale Kraftanstrengung" in Deutschland. Die ab 2. November geltenden Kontaktbeschränkungen seien nötig, um die Kurve der Neuinfektionen wieder abzuflachen. © AFP, EPA

Link zum Video: https://www.faz.net/-gpg-a4wjs
Link zur Homepage: https://www.faz.net

snippet.title: Bund und Länder einigen sich auf weitere Maßnahmen gegen SARS-CoV-2
snippet.description:
Die stetig steigenden Infektionszahlen und auch steigende Zahl von Patienten, die intensivmedizinische Betreuung benötigen, machen weitere Einschränkungen erforderlich, damit sich das Virus nicht weiter unkontrolliert und explosionsartig verbreitet. 

Ministerpräsident Winfried Kretschmann informiert über die Ergebnisse der Beratungen von Bund und Ländern. 


Mehr Informationen: https://www.baden-wuerttemberg.de/de/service/alle-meldungen/meldung/pid/weitere-massnahmen-zur-einschraenkung-der-corona-pandemie/
